- What did you say?

24
00:03:40.540 --> 00:03:45.180
So you can't hear me either?
You're dead. blind and deaf!

25
00:03:45.500 --> 00:03:49.500
Scared? When I can't see a thing.
whom will I be scared of?

26
00:03:52.460 --> 00:03:53.540
I'll deal with them.

27
00:03:55.220 --> 00:03:59.660
Problem with my eyes.
I suddenly stop seeing things.

28
00:03:59.740 --> 00:04:03.580
And problem with my ears.
I'm suddenly hard of hearing.

29
00:04:03.660 --> 00:04:06.380
So when must I put on my hearing-aid..

30
00:04:06.460 --> 00:04:08.620
..and when must I
put on the glasses..?

31
00:04:08.700 --> 00:04:11.700
It all has to do with timing. you see.

32
00:04:22.700 --> 00:04:24.900
Madhav Singh!

33
00:04:38.220 --> 00:04:40.900
Suraj.. Suraj.

34
00:04:41.620 --> 00:04:46.100
Death hovers above my head.

35
00:04:46.660 --> 00:04:51.460
Not your head? Krupa.
It stands before them.

36
00:04:51.940 --> 00:04:56.740
Dressed in a suit.
you want to play a thug. mister?

37
00:05:15.780 --> 00:05:20.060
Is it okay now. Madhav Singh?
- You're not mad. are you?

38
00:05:21.020 --> 00:05:24.460
Aren't you scared of death?
- Only those who love their lives..

39
00:05:25.180 --> 00:05:27.940
..are afraid of death. - Smart-aleck..

40
00:05:34.260 --> 00:05:37.940
Suraj! Don't be afraid!
I'm right here!

41
00:05:38.020 --> 00:05:39.340
I've got your clothes.

42
00:05:55.020 --> 00:05:56.820
They have swords
in their hands. Get in.

43
00:06:17.660 --> 00:06:19.300
Skin them alive!

44
00:06:44.860 --> 00:06:45.540
That's it!

45
00:07:09.740 --> 00:07:10.660
What?

46
00:07:29.740 --> 00:07:31.660
Where have you been? - I went to..

47
00:07:31.900 --> 00:07:34.740
..make Madhav see reason. father.
- To make him see reason?

48
00:07:35.060 --> 00:07:38.420
And what did you finally do?
- What could I do. father..?

49
00:07:38.500 --> 00:07:40.860
Suraj wasn't the one..
who started the fight. brother.

50
00:07:40.940 --> 00:07:43.220
He raised his hands first and Suraj..

51
00:07:43.300 --> 00:07:45.060
Your indulgence has spoiled him.

52
00:07:45.420 --> 00:07:49.860
Why? Don't you love him?
You love him the most.

53
00:07:50.060 --> 00:07:54.060
That's exactly why I'm worried.
Don't ever mess with them again.

54
00:07:55.060 --> 00:07:57.060
Himmat is no small-time thug.

55
00:07:58.500 --> 00:08:02.940
Had something happened to you.
what would your father do?

56
00:08:04.940 --> 00:08:09.580
Suraj..? Balwant Singh's son? - Yes.

57
00:08:09.660 --> 00:08:10.740
Shut up!

58
00:08:14.140 --> 00:08:16.500
He has challenged Himmat's.

59
00:08:17.340 --> 00:08:20.660
I'll have his hands and feet broken..

60
00:08:20.740 --> 00:08:22.740
Cool it. dad.. - Damn you!

61
00:09:27.260 --> 00:09:28.380
Well. I..

62
00:09:31.940 --> 00:09:35.300
Doesn't my girl play
the piano so well?

63
00:09:38.140 --> 00:09:41.820
Why are you staring at her?
Do you recognise her?

64
00:09:42.740 --> 00:09:43.620
Sapna.

65
00:09:47.060 --> 00:09:48.140
You're Suraj. right?

66
00:09:49.140 --> 00:09:52.220
Nice introduction. I say.

67
00:09:52.460 --> 00:09:55.140
No one introduced the
two of you to each other.

68
00:09:55.500 --> 00:09:58.460
