Uncle Cheema is arriving.

71
00:10:03.860 --> 00:10:06.140
She had to be his daughter Sapna.

72
00:10:07.100 --> 00:10:10.020
But how did you recognise her.
my child?

73
00:10:10.460 --> 00:10:13.420
Daddy often says
that his friend's..

74
00:10:13.660 --> 00:10:15.940
