write a few lines now and then.

76
00:10:21.420 --> 00:10:22.780
Hello son!

77
00:10:22.980 --> 00:10:24.740
Suraj! How are you. son?

78
00:10:24.980 --> 00:10:29.500
Come. let's embrace..
that was very satisfying.

79
00:10:29.580 --> 00:10:33.420
Which way have you come in?
- It's him. We went to fetch him.

80
00:10:33.700 --> 00:10:35.340
The guests are already home and..

81
00:10:35.420 --> 00:10:36.740
..this chap was still at the station

82
00:10:37.340 --> 00:10:41.100
