Here I am mourning his death..

92
00:11:07.420 --> 00:11:09.460
..and he stands before me.
How shocking!

93
00:11:14.780 --> 00:11:17.340
Finish your drink.
We must have another.

94
00:11:17.420 --> 00:11:19.340
Before talking about my past..

95
00:11:19.420 --> 00:11:22.540
..do see that my grown
up daughter is right here.

96
00:11:22.620 --> 00:11:25.060
Have you no shame at all?

97
00:11:25.540 --> 00:11:28.740
