106
00:11:50.980 --> 00:11:53.620
Stay over for some more days.
What's your hurry to leave?

107
00:11:53.980 --> 00:11:56.580
I want to stay.
too. but it's necessary..

108
00:11:56.660 --> 00:11:59.500
