109
00:11:59.700 --> 00:12:03.700
But Sapna will stay here.

110
00:12:04.340 --> 00:12:05.460
Yes.

111
00:12:05.540 --> 00:12:08.980
Getting her an admission in
the college is your responsibility.

112
00:12:09.540 --> 00:12:11.340
Rest assured. uncle.
She'll get the admission.

113
00:12:11.420 --> 00:12:12.260
Great!

114
