dishes and washed their clothes.

250
00:26:44.540 --> 00:26:47.380
Know why? For her son.

251
00:26:48.020 --> 00:26:52.100
And the day he grew up.
he left his mother.

252
00:26:53.260 --> 00:26:57.980
Ever since. she goes around
begging like a mad woman.

253
00:26:58.460 --> 00:26:59.580
That's so sad.

254
00:27:00.860 --> 00:27:05.900
What a strange world.
- Yes. it's a strange world.

255
00:27:06.900 --> 00:27:09.260
There are sons walking out on..

256
00:27:09.340 --> 00:27:11.820
..mothers and mothers
leaving their sons.

257
00:27:13.140 --> 00:27:14.020
Suraj.

258
00:27:22.500 --> 00:27:27.180
My word! Fantastic!
- The smell of Bhatinda.

259
00:27:27.860 --> 00:27:33.820
Here you are. Eat this.
- Don't you wait for Suraj at dinner?

260
00:27:34.300 --> 00:27:38.580
Do you want us to starve? - You..

261
00:27:38.660 --> 00:27:40.380
Eat quietly.

262
00:27:41.340 --> 00:27:46.060
Suraj! At nine today?
- Suraj. nice to see you come.

263
00:27:46.300 --> 00:27:48.660
I'm told you've
composed a new couplet.

264
00:27:48.860 --> 00:27:53.180
So recite a couplet.
- Yes! In the forests!

265
00:27:53.260 --> 00:27:54.660
Shut up Jugnu! - Come on Suraj.

266
00:27:55.180 --> 00:28:00.260
Recite a poem. please.
- Go ahead. son. A nice lively one.

267
00:28:00.580 --> 00:28:03.020
To remind my friend
of his younger days.

268
00:28:03.180 --> 00:28:05.980
Any couplet will do.
but not one on booze. Please!

269
00:28:06.060 --> 00:28:07.340
Recite it. Suraj.

270
00:28:07.420 --> 00:28:08.420
Come on. Suraj.

271
00:28:09.340 --> 00:28:10.420
"I was so high on what.."

272
00:28:10.500 --> 00:28:12.380
..I had seen of her last evening.."

273
00:28:13.620 --> 00:28:16.340
"..that my eyes were offended
when sleep took over.."

274
00:28:16.420 --> 00:28:18.620
Fantastic! "I was so high on what.."

275
00:28:18.700 --> 00:28:21.500
"..I had seen of her last evening.."

276
00:28:21.700 --> 00:28:24.020
"That my eyes were offended
when sleep took over.."

277
00:28:24.100 --> 00:28:25.940
Wow! Wow!

278
00:29:06.860 --> 00:29:10.820
"Love.."

279
00:29:10.900 --> 00:29:14.580
"Has happened on the sly.."

280
00:29:14.660 --> 00:29:18.460
"I've sworn it.."

281
00:29:18.540 --> 00:29:21.940
"Ever so secretly.."

282
00:29:22.020 --> 00:29:28.980
"On the sly.."

283
00:29:29.740 --> 00:29:37.420
"The world will never get wind.."

284
00:29:37.580 --> 00:29:44.940
"When we meet secretly.."

285
00:29:45.220 --> 00:29:48.940
"Love.."

286
00:29:49.100 --> 00:29:52.820
"Has happened on the sly.."

287
00:29:52.900 --> 00:29:56.420
"I've sworn it.."

288
00:29:56.660 --> 00:30:00.500
"Ever so secretly.."

289
00:30:28.940 --> 00:30:36.700
"We'll let our eyes
speak for our hearts.."

290
00:30:36.780 --> 00:30:44.380
"To our lips.
we shall not bring a word.."

291
00:30:44.460 --> 00:30:51.980
"Pining. loneliness.."

292
00:30:52.060 --> 00:30:59.500
"we'll together put up with.."

293
00:30:59.580 --> 00:31:06.940
"Desire gives me a beautiful grief.."

294
00:31:07.020 --> 00:31:14.220
"This grief I shall
bear secretly too."

295
00:31:47.260 --> 00:31:54.900
"Ever since I have seen you.
my love.."

296
00:31:54.980 --> 00:32:02.500
"I have turned a
poet at first sight.."

297
00:32:02.660 --> 00:32:10.220
"I have hidden you away.."

298
00:32:10.300 --> 00:32:17.700
"in my heart. in my eyes.."

299
00:32:17.780 --> 00:32:25.340
"Without you. I find peace nowhere.."

300
00:32:25.420 --> 00:32:32.820
"Such is the state
you have brought me to.."

301
00:32:32.900 --> 00:32:40.420
"Love has happened on the sly.."

302
00:32:40.500 --> 00:32:48.420
"I've sworn it ever so secretly.."

303
00:32:56.060 --> 00:33:01.140
She said that liquor is
evil and you gave up drinking!

304
00:33:02.100 --> 00:33:04.620
But I'm keeping you company. - No!

305
00:33:04.860 --> 00:33:06.620
Even if a drinker
stops going to the bar..

306
00:33:06.700 --> 00:33:09.180
..he never gives up drinking.

307
00:33:09.700 --> 00:33:14.220
Tell Sapna that you're
in love with her.

308
00:33:16.100 --> 00:33:20.100
Don't delay it anymore. my friend.
Make a booking at once.

309
00:33:20.380 --> 00:33:24.860
Or you might see her hooked elsewhere.

310
00:33:28.660 --> 00:33:30.660
Welcome sir.

311
00:33:34.340 --> 00:33:38.300
How much money?
- Bachelor? I'm married.

312
00:33:39.900 --> 00:33:44.900
So you're a bit hard of hearing?
- Hard up? It's 1300 rupees!

313
00:33:45.100 --> 00:33:49.620
1300 ? So little?
I'll give you 200 more. A tip.

314
00:33:49.700 --> 00:33:54.500
1500 makes nice hearing. right?
- 1500 ? One moment.

315
00:34:05.500 --> 00:34:06.940
Maybe it's in the other pocket.

316
00:34:11.820 --> 00:34:12.940
Maybe in the third.

317
00:34:19.940 --> 00:34:21.140
No pocket at all.

318
00:34:22.900 --> 00:34:25.780
Looks like my wallet has been picked.

319
00:34:33.100 --> 00:34:36.620
Look. mister.
I've started business only today..

320
00:34:36.699 --> 00:34:40.779
and you're my first passenger.
So please skip these nasty jokes.

321
00:34:41.100 --> 00:34:43.620
I'll have a heart-attack
and you'll be..

322
00:34:43.699 --> 00:34:45.899
.. imprisoned for killing me. My fare.

323
00:34:46.219 --> 00:34:50.179
Strange man!
You're worried about your fare.

324
00:34:50.260 --> 00:34:53.060
I've been relieved
of 500 500-rupee notes.

325
00:34:53.300 --> 00:34:55.100
And you no sympathies at all.

326
00:34:56.260 --> 00:34:58.980
I think I have to show my
sympathy to him now. One moment.

327
00:34:59.060 --> 00:35:02.100
Friends. come here. come here.

328
00:35:03.260 --> 00:35:06.700
This man has lost his purse.
Show him some sympathy. please.

329
00:35:08.140 --> 00:35:09.620
He hasn't any money to pay the fare..

330
00:35:09.700 --> 00:35:11.940
..Show him some sympathy. please.

331
00:35:12.020 --> 00:35:16.460
How much was the fare. Jugnu?
- 1500 rupees.

332
00:35:16.540 --> 00:35:19.860
1000 was the fare.
200 was the tip.. - What tip?

333
00:35:19.940 --> 00:35:23.100
I don't have money to pay the fare..
- You yourself told me!

334
00:35:23.180 --> 00:35:28.140
He made me spend on cigarettes.
said he didn't have any change.

335
00:35:28.220 --> 00:35:30.740
And now he says the wallet is missing.
Beat him up!

336
00:35:30.820 --> 00:35:32.300
What kind of a person are you?

337
00:35:32.780 --> 00:35:35.620
It's just money..
- I'll not spare you.

338
00:35:36.700 --> 00:35:41.060
Wait.. how much money is it?
- You'll pay for him. Suraj?

339
00:35:41.140 --> 00:35:42.700
I've been watching the farce.

340
00:35:42.780 --> 00:35:44.180
Such a thing could happen to anyone.

341
00:35:44.260 --> 00:35:46.500
Don't you see?
He appears to come from a nice family.

342
00:35:46.580 --> 00:35:50.380
Right. big brother.
I really come from a decent family.

343
00:35:50.460 --> 00:35:55.020
Or I'd have paid him. I was
even carrying my credit cards in it.

344
00:35:55.940 --> 00:35:58.260
How much money. uncle? - 1500 rupees.

345
00:35:58.580 --> 00:36:03.700
1500 for what? Deduct 200 from it.
- All right. give me 1300.

346
00:36:04.700 --> 00:36:05.780
1500.

347
00:36:06.700 --> 00:36:07.500
Take this.

348
00:36:07.740 --> 00:36:10.100
I'll fix you. - What? What?

349
00:36:13.420 --> 00:36:18.300
Brother.. where are you going?
Give me your address. please.

350
00:36:18.660 --> 00:36:21.020
I've got to return your money.
- No. it's all right.

351
00:36:21.100 --> 00:36:25.060
Oh no. how's that possible.
I come from a respectable family.

352
00:36:25.140 --> 00:36:28.100
Please give me your card.
I'll return your money to you.

353
00:36:28.180 --> 00:36:30.380
I promise. - Here.

354
00:36:30.460 --> 00:36:32.700
Thank you. Thank you for your help.

355
00:36:37.620 --> 00:36:43.060
Suraj Singh.
Partner. Gun Park Royal Hotel.

356
00:36:44.300 --> 00:36:46.220
Here's your money.

357
00:36:47.740 --> 00:36:50.300
Here's your salary for today.
You needn't come tomorrow.

358
00:36:50.380 --> 00:36:52.900
Why? - Suraj paid up today.

359
00:36:52.980 --> 00:36:53.940
Who's going to pay up tomorrow?

360
00:36:58.500 --> 00:36:59.780
Damn you!

361
00:36:59.940 --> 00:37:03.660
Raj Chauhan.. you must have
a booking in my name. - Sorry sir.

362
00:37:03.860 --> 00:37:06.340
There's no booking in your name.
- Are you sure?

363
00:37:07.500 --> 00:37:09.980
Where's that bloody Suraj..?
- Sir. excuse me.

364
00:37:10.340 --> 00:37:13.980
You're talking about our boss.
- Boss. he is to you.

365
00:37:14.060 --> 00:37:19.780
He's my childhood friend.
I'll give him such a tight slap.

366
00:37:20.100 --> 00:37:23.100
He begs me to come here and
doesn't even come to receive me.

367
00:37:23.180 --> 00:37:26.020
And there isn't even a room for me!
Isn't it wrong..?

368
00:37:27.180 --> 00:37:28.180
It is wrong sir.

369
00:37:28.260 --> 00:37:31.220
Mr Gupta.
looks like Mr Suraj forgot to tell..

370
00:37:31.300 --> 00:37:33.020
..us about his friend's arrival.

371
00:37:33.380 --> 00:37:37.420
But he has even given up drinking.
- Maybe that's why he forgot.

372
00:37:37.500 --> 00:37:38.060
Okay.

373
00:37:38.140 --> 00:37:42.060
If he goes away.
you might even lose your job. sir.

374
00:37:42.140 --> 00:37:44.620
I'm leaving. This is an insult.
- Sir. sir. Excuse me. sir.

375
00:37:45.380 --> 00:37:47.420
Didn't you talk about a room. sir?

376
00:37:47.500 --> 00:37:49.860
Actually there's a suite
booked in your name. sir.

377
00:37:50.580 --> 00:37:52.020
Go and get it ready.

378
00:37:52.100 --> 00:37:54.700
I like that. I like that.
I like you. - Thank you sir.

379
00:37:54.780 --> 00:37:58.260
You hide your boss's weakness.
Nice employee.

380
00:37:58.420 --> 00:38:00.700
Thank you sir.
- All right. I'll take the suite.

381
00:38:01.100 --> 00:38:04.100
But don't tell Suraj I'm staying here

382
00:38:04.420 --> 00:38:07.460
No. - I want to see
when he thinks of me.

383
00:38:07.540 --> 00:38:08.380
Right sir.

384
00:38:08.940 --> 00:38:11.940
Don't shake your head.
For your father's sake. you mustn't.

385
00:38:18.020 --> 00:38:18.860
Sir.

386
00:38:20.460 --> 00:38:23.860
Looks like you forgot
to tell us about your friend.

387
00:38:24.140 --> 00:38:27.340
But I've given him a suite.
- My friend..?

388
00:38:28.100 --> 00:38:29.300
Raja..?

389
00:38:30.900 --> 00:38:35.940
Please don't tell him that
I've already reminded you. sir.

390
00:38:36.420 --> 00:38:38.380
He has implored me
in the name of my father.

391
00:38:39.460 --> 00:38:44.260
Implored you?
- My father's dead. sir..

392
00:38:44.340 --> 00:38:46.300
..won't make a difference
if I break my promise

393
00:38:46.580 --> 00:38:49.340
All right.
The suite. isn't it? - Yes. sir.

394
00:38:49.940 --> 00:38:54.100
Keep it. Keep it. Come in.

395
00:38:54.260 --> 00:38:55.780
The door won't open on the outside.

396
00:38:56.260 --> 00:38:58.140
Open it. You want me to open it then?

397
00:39:05.740 --> 00:39:06.940
I'll explain this. sir..

398
00:39:07.380 --> 00:39:09.460
..what are you guys watching?
Get going!

399
00:39:09.540 --> 00:39:12.300
Stay.. throw his stuff out.

400
00:39:13.140 --> 00:39:15.220
Let's sort it out between ourselves.

401
00:39:15.380 --> 00:39:18.740
I want them to see
how I deal with frauds.

402
00:39:18.820 --> 00:39:21.580
I was hungry. sir.
And I'm even willing to do the dishes.

403
00:39:21.660 --> 00:39:25.020
Really? Throw it out.
- What are you doing..?

404
00:39:25.180 --> 00:39:28.100
Don't have it thrown. sir.
- You throw it out then.

405
00:39:28.180 --> 00:39:29.660
I have stuff in it. sir. - Throw it!

406
00:39:31.100 --> 00:39:34.260
Was there anything else?
- My respect. sir. And you..

407
00:39:34.340 --> 00:39:36.740
Respect?
- I come from a nice family. sir.

408
00:39:36.820 --> 00:39:39.260
Nice family. eh? Rotten..

409
00:39:40.060 --> 00:39:42.940
Sorry sir. I got hurt in my eye.

410
00:39:43.540 --> 00:39:44.900
You. son?

411
00:39:44.980 --> 00:39:48.540
Uncle Rastogi! How are you? - Fine.

412
00:39:48.780 --> 00:39:50.580
Mr. Rastogi. do you know him?
- Of course.

413
00:39:50.660 --> 00:39:54.180
He's from a rich family in Jaipur.
He has a huge bungalow there.

414
00:39:54.260 --> 00:39:56.900
Yes. tell them.
- Are you here on a vacation. son?

415
00:39:57.260 --> 00:40:00.020
If someone lets me have a vacation.

416
00:40:00.100 --> 00:40:05.340
The hills are very beautiful.
- And dangerous too.

417
00:40:05.540 --> 00:40:08.380
Enjoy yourself. young man.
Enjoy yourself. - Bye.

418
00:40:08.820 --> 00:40:09.860
Hear that?

419
00:40:11.340 --> 00:40:13.180
Come on in. You may go.

420
00:40:14.380 --> 00:40:17.740
Excuse me. With or without luggage?

421
00:40:18.060 --> 00:40:19.300
Bring it all in.

422
00:40:20.300 --> 00:40:21.380
Thank you.

423
00:40:22.460 --> 00:40:25.380
Now look. Maybe you come from
a decent family.. - Big brother..

424
00:40:26.980 --> 00:40:27.700
Got hurt.

425
00:40:28.420 --> 00:40:32.700
You've always come to my
rescue like an elder brother.

426
00:40:33.660 --> 00:40:38.140
May I call you Big Brother?
- Certainly.

427
00:40:38.380 --> 00:40:39.420
Thank you. thank you.

428
00:40:39.860 --> 00:40:43.460
The problem is.
mother's forcing me into a marriage.

429
00:40:43.540 --> 00:40:47.100
And there's someone else I love.
- Where is the girl?

430
00:40:47.700 --> 00:40:51.060
I don't know.
but I'm told she's in this very city.

431
00:40:51.380 --> 00:40:55.140
Big Brother. in just one glimpse..

432
00:40:56.340 --> 00:41:00.100
..I gave my heart away to her.

433
00:41:10.420 --> 00:41:13.700
You saw her at the fashion show.
You must've taken pictures too?

434
00:41:15.220 --> 00:41:19.580
If only I could gather my wits.
I'd surely have taken pictures.

435
00:41:20.860 --> 00:41:22.620
I was blown out.

436
00:41:26.020 --> 00:41:29.020
Strange. isn't it?
But this is how matters..

437
00:41:29.740 --> 00:41:33.540
..of the heart are. Big Brother.

438
00:41:47.780 --> 00:41:49.220
Deep in thought. eh?

439
00:41:49.820 --> 00:41:52.700
From the look of it.
you are in love with someone too.

440
00:41:53.300 --> 00:41:54.860
I was thinking what a fool you are.

441
00:41:55.260 --> 00:41:56.420
You don't know where the girl lives..

442
00:41:56.500 --> 00:41:58.620
..and you're out to find her.
How will you?

443
00:41:58.820 --> 00:42:02.340
With your help. If you help me..

444
00:42:02.420 --> 00:42:04.860
..my work will be done. Big Brother.

445
00:42:05.300 --> 00:42:07.300
It has to do with love.. okay?

446
00:42:08.580 --> 00:42:11.300
What are you doing here?
- What are you doing here?

447
00:42:11.380 --> 00:42:15.540
What a look you cast at my taxi
I had to close down that business..

448
00:42:15.620 --> 00:42:20.140
..and I start a canteen here.
- Here? I see.

449
00:42:20.220 --> 00:42:23.260
You've followed me.
here to torment me.

450
00:42:23.340 --> 00:42:25.420
Who gave you my whereabouts?

451
00:42:25.500 --> 00:42:27.580
Why did you come into
my life again? Why..?

452
00:42:27.660 --> 00:42:29.420
What harm have I done to you?

453
00:42:29.500 --> 00:42:32.460
You're the one who
came into my life. - Me..?

454
00:42:32.540 --> 00:42:33.340
Yes.

455
00:42:35.820 --> 00:42:38.060
We weren't related in
our previous birth. were we?

456
00:42:38.500 --> 00:42:40.580
We aren't brothers
lost in the fair. are we?

457
00:42:40.660 --> 00:42:45.460
There! You spoke my heart!

458
00:42:45.780 --> 00:42:48.300
Brother! My brother!

459
00:42:49.100 --> 00:42:50.140
My brother!

460
00:42:51.500 --> 00:42:55.620
If we are brothers.
we ought to help each other. Right?

461
00:42:55.740 --> 00:42:57.740
Who's doing what to whom? - You.

462
00:42:57.820 --> 00:42:59.660
What..? - Help me.

463
00:43:00.940 --> 00:43:04.100
All right.
Which girl are you here to bother?

464
00:43:08.580 --> 00:43:11.100
How did you know I'm
here to bother a girl?

465
00:43:11.260 --> 00:43:15.420
It shows on your face.
- I looked tired. don't I?

466
00:43:16.060 --> 00:43:19.660
Just two women's colleges in the city.
One. I've checked out.

467
00:43:19.740 --> 00:43:23.460
She ought to be here then. right?
- Yes. Exactly!

468
00:43:24.220 --> 00:43:27.500
She must be here.
Find her. And tease her!

469
00:43:27.580 --> 00:43:33.580
But please let me run my canteen!
Let me sell my snacks!

470
00:43:34.220 --> 00:43:34.980
Listen.

471
00:43:40.180 --> 00:43:41.180
What luck man!

472
00:43:41.260 --> 00:43:43.020
So you told her. right?

473
00:43:43.740 --> 00:43:44.700
Hi.

474
00:43:44.780 --> 00:43:46.220
He is calling you.
isn't he? - Hi.

475
00:43:47.220 --> 00:43:50.660
Hi Sapna.
Haven't you recognized me? - No

476
00:43:50.740 --> 00:43:53.700
That's strange. Everything's
fine back home in Bhatinda. I hope?

477
00:43:54.260 --> 00:43:56.900
Yes. but I haven't..
- You don't recognize me. right?

478
00:43:57.660 --> 00:44:01.500
How would you?
We were never introduced.

479
00:44:02.260 --> 00:44:04.780
I saw you at the fashion
show - Who is he?

480
00:44:04.860 --> 00:44:07.500
You're the one I've
been looking for ever since.

481
00:44:07.940 --> 00:44:11.300
When I set out from home.
I was carrying 200.000 rupees.

482
00:44:11.380 --> 00:44:15.740
And now. I have nothing.
- You want to borrow money from her?

483
00:44:15.820 --> 00:44:17.260
Don't be silly.

484
00:44:17.340 --> 00:44:20.380
I only wanted to tell her
that I can do anything for her.

485
00:44:20.460 --> 00:44:23.380
Really? Anything? - Of course.

486
00:44:23.460 --> 00:44:26.660
I can even die for her.
- No. don't die for her.

487
00:44:26.740 --> 00:44:28.500
Or she'll be arrested.

488
00:44:28.660 --> 00:44:29.740
Very funny.

489
00:44:30.260 --> 00:44:32.260
So you can do anything for me?
- Of course.

490
00:44:33.140 --> 00:44:34.340
See that man?

491
00:44:34.980 --> 00:44:35.540
Good morning. sir.

492
00:44:35.620 --> 00:44:37.980
Good morning. How
are you. students?

493
00:44:38.060 --> 00:44:39.700
Just get me his hat.

494
00:44:41.700 --> 00:44:44.460
You think you can't? - No.

495
00:44:44.620 --> 00:44:48.220
I was thinking what
a trivia you asked me to do.

496
00:44:48.300 --> 00:44:52.540
His hat. isn't it?
Not his trousers. I hope.

497
00:44:52.620 --> 00:44:54.500
I'll get it. Uncle.

498
00:44:54.580 --> 00:44:56.700
The principal isn't sparing him.

499
00:44:57.900 --> 00:45:00.180
Our college is participating
in the dance-competition too.

500
00:45:00.260 --> 00:45:01.660
Okay? Happy?

501
00:45:03.660 --> 00:45:04.980
Be prepared.

502
00:45:07.340 --> 00:45:08.700
Don't be nervous. - Hello. Uncle.

503
00:45:09.380 --> 00:45:12.100
Hello. You're wearing a nice hat.
Will you give it to me?

504
00:45:12.340 --> 00:45:12.940
What?

505
00:45:13.260 --> 00:45:14.980
Hello aunty. - Aunty?

506
00:45:15.220 --> 00:45:16.580
What is this nonsense. Catch him!

507
00:45:17.140 --> 00:45:18.820
Let go..

508
00:45:19.260 --> 00:45:20.140
Sapna! - Call the police.

509
00:45:24.780 --> 00:45:27.740
There was a call from the police
station. They've arrested some boy.

510
00:45:28.380 --> 00:45:33.060
What have I to do with him?
- He says you're his elder brother.

511
00:45:33.140 --> 00:45:34.700
He's even carrying your business card.

512
00:45:37.180 --> 00:45:39.260
Why did I give that lover-boy my card?

513
00:45:39.340 --> 00:45:43.660
My son has returned to me.
Suraj has given me money for sweets.

514
00:45:50.300 --> 00:45:52.780
Lady..

515
00:46:45.820 --> 00:46:48.820
You killed the poor woman!
You killed her!

516
00:46:49.740 --> 00:46:50.740
You killed the poor woman!

517
00:46:51.500 --> 00:46:53.340
You killed the poor woman!

518
00:46:59.260 --> 00:47:02.180
Get up! You killed the poor woman!

519
00:47:02.260 --> 00:47:06.020
Suraj! Suraj!
- He killed the poor woman!

520
00:47:06.860 --> 00:47:08.340
Don't take the law in your hands.

521
00:47:09.860 --> 00:47:10.780
Look at this. sir.

522
00:47:12.660 --> 00:47:15.300
Drugs and weapons. - Bastard!

523
00:47:15.380 --> 00:47:20.180
Inspector. You don't know me.
I'm Himmat's son.

524
00:47:20.260 --> 00:47:23.300
Don't! Don't! Don't do this!

525
00:47:24.060 --> 00:47:25.140
Take him away.

526
00:47:26.460 --> 00:47:27.460
Hello. Khan sir.

527
00:47:30.380 --> 00:47:32.180
Hello!

528
00:47:32.860 --> 00:47:34.620
I must compliment your courage.

529
00:47:35.740 --> 00:47:38.780
The courage to arrest
Himmat's son.

530
00:47:40.660 --> 00:47:44.740
So much courage the cops must have.
or who will respect them?

531
00:47:46.820 --> 00:47:48.740
Really. Khan sir. I
liked it very much.

532
00:47:49.340 --> 00:47:51.420
Because he's Himmat's son.
he can't do anything. can he?

533
00:47:53.340 --> 00:47:55.580
Because his father
is respected in the city..

534
00:47:55.660 --> 00:47:56.860
..must he be respected too?

535
00:47:57.260 --> 00:47:58.820
It's good that you arrested him.

536
00:47:59.100 --> 00:48:00.700
It'll drill some sense into him.

537
00:48:03.060 --> 00:48:04.580
But in these five hours..

538
00:48:05.060 --> 00:48:07.660
..he must've come back to his senses.
Inspector.

539
00:48:07.820 --> 00:48:09.460
The law is not a joke.

540
00:48:11.380 --> 00:48:16.620
He's a kid. Khan sir.
And kids to make mistakes.

541
00:48:16.700 --> 00:48:20.220
That is when elders like
us have to do something about it.

542
00:48:20.980 --> 00:48:24.060
So what are we going to do. Khan sir?
- It's difficult right now.

543
00:48:25.700 --> 00:48:27.300
Nothing can happen before Monday.

544
00:48:28.900 --> 00:48:30.060
Monday..?

545
00:48:31.020 --> 00:48:33.460
We can't help it. Himmat.
It's not in our hands.

546
00:48:35.660 --> 00:48:40.940
The job of the police is
to make arrests. To release them..

547
00:48:41.900 --> 00:48:44.620
is the job of the judge in the court.
- That's what you think

548
00:48:45.180 --> 00:48:49.580
Others can do that too.
You know who does it..?

549
00:48:50.500 --> 00:48:51.460
Wait. I'll show you.

550
00:49:01.100 --> 00:49:03.860
I knew you'd telephone
some scoundrel or the other..

551
00:49:04.500 --> 00:49:06.220
..and he'd put pressure
on Inspector Khan.

552
00:49:06.820 --> 00:49:08.420
Which is why I didn't
leave this place.

553
00:49:09.860 --> 00:49:12.300
You can make that call
even after you leave this place.

554
00:49:12.740 --> 00:49:14.020
But remember..

555
00:49:14.900 --> 00:49:19.140
..even if your son is let off
from here. he won't escape from me.

556
00:49:22.500 --> 00:49:25.260
Who are you?
- I'm the old woman's son.

557
00:49:27.020 --> 00:49:31.620
So what are you going
to do to my son? What..?

558
00:49:32.340 --> 00:49:36.820
Do you know who I am?
Himmat. That's my name.

559
00:49:37.260 --> 00:49:42.660
Have you heard that name?
- I heard your son uttering it.

560
00:49:43.220 --> 00:49:44.460
I beat him up very badly.

561
00:49:44.900 --> 00:49:47.340
And then I heard
Madhav Singh saying it.

562
00:49:47.660 --> 00:49:51.580
I gave him a thrashing too.
Hasn't he told you..?

563
00:49:51.660 --> 00:49:53.660
Save me from this chap. Pops!

564
00:49:53.740 --> 00:49:56.340
And this box! This box Pops.

565
00:49:56.900 --> 00:49:58.300
So you are Suraj..?

566
00:50:01.140 --> 00:50:02.660
All right. All right.

567
00:50:02.820 --> 00:50:07.300
If I forgive your mistake once..
you find a lot of courage. eh?

568
00:50:10.180 --> 00:50:11.860
Men are born with courage.

569
00:50:13.020 --> 00:50:14.580
Merely calling yourself
himmat (courage)..

570
00:50:14.900 --> 00:50:17.940
..doesn't make you courageous.
- Shankar. get the car out.

571
00:50:18.380 --> 00:50:20.140
Don't go away. We'll leave together.

572
00:50:21.220 --> 00:50:26.820
I'll have my son freed..
and I'm not sparing you.

573
00:50:27.860 --> 00:50:28.740
Let's go.

574
00:50:34.020 --> 00:50:38.780
Here you are. For your welfare fund.
A humble present.

575
00:50:41.540 --> 00:50:44.740
5 million? Is it a bribe?

576
00:50:44.820 --> 00:50:46.420
How can you say that. Thakur sir?

577
00:50:46.500 --> 00:50:48.220
It's meant for your welfare fund.

578
00:50:48.300 --> 00:50:50.740
It'll help the poor. - Very well.

579
00:50:51.260 --> 00:50:53.180
Okay. - Yes sir.

580
00:50:53.860 --> 00:50:54.740
Good bye.

581
00:50:56.380 --> 00:50:57.820
Greetings. Thakur sir.

582
00:50:57.980 --> 00:51:00.060
We've brought offerings
for you from Shirdi.

583
00:51:00.420 --> 00:51:03.380
Thanks to Him. the work
at the ashram has begun again.

584
00:51:03.460 --> 00:51:06.220
The builder has withdrawn
the court's stay order.

585
00:51:06.300 --> 00:51:08.980
I know that. - The oblations.

586
00:51:13.900 --> 00:51:17.060
Trivedi.
have this cheque deposited today.

587
00:51:17.260 --> 00:51:18.820
Call from Himmat.

588
00:51:20.180 --> 00:51:22.860
Go on. Himmat.
- How are you. Thakur sir?

589
00:51:22.940 --> 00:51:26.540
Let's talk business.
- My son has been arrested.

590
00:51:27.340 --> 00:51:31.300
So what's new? Such things
keep happening in our business.

591
00:51:33.700 --> 00:51:36.940
In any case. your son has gone
mad after taking all those drugs.

592
00:51:37.380 --> 00:51:38.580
If he spends a few days in lock-up..

593
00:51:38.660 --> 00:51:40.020
..he'll surely come to his senses.

594
00:51:40.100 --> 00:51:41.580
But I depended on you and made..

595
00:51:41.660 --> 00:51:43.380
..tall claims at the police station.

596
00:51:44.140 --> 00:51:46.820
If you don't help me. my son will..

597
00:51:47.020 --> 00:51:50.700
Don't get sentimental.
And don't forget..

598
00:51:50.780 --> 00:51:54.060
..you're looking after my interests.
It isn't the other way around

599
00:51:54.820 --> 00:51:56.740
Forget him and come to me immediately.

600
00:51:56.820 --> 00:51:59.460
Sir. if I come over to Delhi.
my son Gogi..

601
00:51:59.540 --> 00:52:01.780
Take the first flight and come to me.

602
00:52:03.460 --> 00:52:06.020
Thakur sir. hats off to you!
Delhi is in your clutches.

603
00:52:06.100 --> 00:52:08.220
If there's anyone
in the country more..

604
00:52:08.300 --> 00:52:09.980
..powerful than the Prime Minister..

605
00:52:10.060 --> 00:52:13.500
It's you! You have saved
my government from being toppled.

606
00:52:14.380 --> 00:52:17.420
Looks like you've become a minister.
- All thanks to you. sir!

607
00:52:17.500 --> 00:52:19.900
You are henceforth
my lord and I'm your slave.

608
00:52:27.540 --> 00:52:29.420
Please pack this. - Yes. go ahead.

609
00:52:29.500 --> 00:52:35.100
And.. - Aunt. you said Suraj never
helped out with domestic affairs.

610
00:52:35.180 --> 00:52:37.700
But look at him.
He's even choosing jewellery.

611
00:52:38.340 --> 00:52:41.420
Oh yes! There's a sea change in Suraj.

612
00:52:41.500 --> 00:52:44.900
And why..?
Only he knows. Show me that one.

613
00:52:44.980 --> 00:52:46.780
How's this one?
- How much is it worth?

614
00:52:46.860 --> 00:52:51.860
Sapna. buy some jewellery
for yourself. - Yes. Sapna. Go ahead.

615
00:52:52.220 --> 00:52:54.980
No. I'm not fond of jeweler.

616
00:52:55.060 --> 00:52:57.380
But you will wear some very soon.

617
00:52:57.460 --> 00:53:00.660
If you don't make a choice.
someone will choose for you. Right?

618
00:53:00.900 --> 00:53:02.500
Aunty. you..

619
00:53:15.020 --> 00:53:17.700
Lovely necklace.
Whom are you buying it for?

620
00:53:19.260 --> 00:53:21.740
For you. - What?

621
00:53:23.140 --> 00:53:24.780
Try it on.

622
00:53:26.860 --> 00:53:27.980
Put it around my neck.

623
00:53:41.820 --> 00:53:47.100
Wow! How does it look?
- It looks beautiful now.

624
00:53:51.100 --> 00:53:52.340
Mr Suraj..

625
00:53:55.620 --> 00:53:56.940
Mr Suraj..

626
00:54:00.460 --> 00:54:04.420
Want me to pack this? - Put this away.

627
00:54:04.860 --> 00:54:06.220
I'll pick it up later.

628
00:54:07.780 --> 00:54:10.980
What will you have? - Pepsi

629
00:54:11.420 --> 00:54:12.980
You? - Pepsi?

630
00:54:13.380 --> 00:54:16.580
Really? I'll have a coffee.

631
00:54:24.980 --> 00:54:31.100
This boy's been bothering
me for so many days. Take a look..

632
00:54:33.220 --> 00:54:34.060
Oh God!

633
00:54:36.100 --> 00:54:38.940
Want me to fix him..? Wait a moment.

634
00:54:41.820 --> 00:54:48.460
So spoilt brat!
She's the girl. isn't she?

635
00:54:48.540 --> 00:54:51.740
You will tease our girl. will you?

636
00:54:53.300 --> 00:54:55.180
Your girl? - Yes.

637
00:54:55.700 --> 00:54:58.500
She neither looks like you.
nor behaves like you.

638
00:54:59.460 --> 00:55:01.740
And who's the one who
has gone away to Canada?

639
00:55:02.900 --> 00:55:05.300
So you've made all enquiries!

640
00:55:05.580 --> 00:55:08.660
Even if she's his daughter.
she's our responsibility!

641
00:55:09.020 --> 00:55:14.420
You will tease our girl..? - Uncle!

642
00:55:14.660 --> 00:55:17.820
Why're you folding your trousers?
- It's easier to run away.

643
00:55:17.900 --> 00:55:21.540
How do you know?
Only those who are guilty. run away!

644
00:55:21.620 --> 00:55:24.340
I'm not sparing you!
- And I'm not letting go of her.

645
00:55:24.420 --> 00:55:26.580
So you're challenging me! - Sure.

646
00:55:26.660 --> 00:55:28.900
All right. I'll deal with you! - Ok.

647
00:55:55.060 --> 00:56:04.900
"Love.."

648
00:56:09.340 --> 00:56:14.140
"Come into my life. my love"

649
00:56:14.220 --> 00:56:18.820
"Bring fragrance to
my life with your love"

650
00:56:18.900 --> 00:56:23.540
"Come into my life. my love"

651
00:56:23.620 --> 00:56:27.700
"Never leave my life ever"

652
00:56:27.780 --> 00:56:37.260
"Love.."

653
00:56:37.340 --> 00:56:47.260
"Love.."

654
00:57:07.260 --> 00:57:11.300
"Your beauty torments me all night"

655
00:57:11.460 --> 00:57:15.980
"You are the one
I dream of all the time"

656
00:57:16.500 --> 00:57:20.700
"It isn't easy to trap
me with your sweet words"

657
00:57:20.780 --> 00:57:25.420
"I'm no butterfly anyone
can lay his hands on"

658
00:57:25.860 --> 00:57:35.060
"Love.."

659
00:57:35.300 --> 00:57:43.700
"Love.."

660
00:58:12.500 --> 00:58:16.420
"My love is meant for the one.."

661
00:58:16.500 --> 00:58:21.100
"who will belong to
me through seven lifetimes"

662
00:58:21.260 --> 00:58:25.740
"So much of love I have
for you in my heart. my love.."

663
00:58:26.020 --> 00:58:30.700
"even a hundred lifetimes won't
be enough to give it all to you"

664
00:58:40.660 --> 00:58:49.740
"Love.."

665
00:58:55.300 --> 00:58:56.380
What am I to do with you?

666
00:58:58.460 --> 00:59:01.140
Please arrange for my bail.
Big Brother.

667
00:59:01.620 --> 00:59:04.620
So you'll land behind bars again?
Do you like it there?

668
00:59:04.700 --> 00:59:08.180
Not at all.
I'm the first man in my family..

669
00:59:08.940 --> 00:59:10.820
..to ever have been behind bars.

670
00:59:12.260 --> 00:59:15.300
Introduce me to the girl.

671
00:59:15.380 --> 00:59:16.500
I'll talk to her on your behalf.

672
00:59:16.580 --> 00:59:18.540
Let me at least bring
her around first.

673
00:59:18.780 --> 00:59:22.580
I'll introduce you afterwards.
- Khan. please forgive this lover.

674
00:59:22.940 --> 00:59:25.340
I'll come this evening
to sign the bail papers.

675
00:59:25.420 --> 00:59:26.340
Okay.

676
00:59:30.780 --> 00:59:33.660
Say a proper job.
I've found a new job. - Yes.

677
00:59:33.860 --> 00:59:36.260
"Hail divine Mother.."

678
00:59:36.340 --> 00:59:38.700
Softly.. I can hear you.

679
00:59:39.700 --> 00:59:44.740
What's the prayer for. uncle?
- As my mother said..

680
00:59:45.500 --> 00:59:48.020
when there is no way.
set out on one path.

681
00:59:48.260 --> 00:59:49.780
You will find your goal.

682
00:59:50.260 --> 00:59:54.100
But you know what your goal is.
A job.. and the sack.

683
00:59:54.300 --> 01:00:00.700
So what's the prayer for?
- To make money! Lots of money!

684
01:00:01.180 --> 01:00:04.260
Money? What for?
- I've got to get two guys bumped off.

685
01:00:04.900 --> 01:00:09.060
Which two guys?
- One. I can do nothing about.

686
01:00:09.140 --> 01:00:12.500
The other is the guy who bails
this chap out. when he's arrested.

687
01:00:13.700 --> 01:00:16.860
Who's it?
- That vagabond. that loafer!

688
01:00:16.940 --> 01:00:22.260
Who teases Sapna at the college.
- Who is he?

689
01:00:22.500 --> 01:00:25.060
He's the one you
paid the taxi fare for.

690
01:00:25.140 --> 01:00:26.940
That fraud who claims
to come from a decent family.

691
01:00:27.220 --> 01:00:29.340
He has made life miserable for Sapna.

692
01:00:29.540 --> 01:00:32.260
She won't even look at him..

693
01:00:32.340 --> 01:00:35.900
..and this shameless chap
won't stop bothering her!

694
01:00:35.980 --> 01:00:38.380
Gupta. where is Raja? - Sir..

695
01:00:38.460 --> 01:00:39.460
Where's Raja?

696
01:00:39.780 --> 01:00:40.460
You..?

697
01:00:41.420 --> 01:00:44.060
Why are you here?
Want to get me kicked out of here too?

698
01:00:44.140 --> 01:00:47.460
Go away! - No Jugnu.

699
01:00:47.540 --> 01:00:53.820
I just want Sapna's address.
- Why? To go and flirt with her?

700
01:00:53.900 --> 01:00:55.620
Try doing that!
- You're taking me wrong.

701
01:00:55.700 --> 01:00:57.860
Not to flirt. I want to make her mine.

702
01:00:58.780 --> 01:01:00.220
I belong to an aristocratic family.

703
01:01:00.300 --> 01:01:03.180
Really? - Give me her address.
I swear..

704
01:01:03.260 --> 01:01:05.540
I'll see to it that your
job gets confirmed in my company.

705
01:01:05.620 --> 01:01:07.460
Really? Now look mister..

706
01:01:07.540 --> 01:01:09.660
..if you belong to an
aristocratic family. I'm no less.

707
01:01:09.740 --> 01:01:12.300
I wouldn't stoop so low for a job.
- Listen.

708
01:01:12.380 --> 01:01:15.340
Nonsense!
- You're misunderstanding me.

709
01:01:15.420 --> 01:01:18.220
Now go away. Else.
you'll see the worst of me.

710
01:01:18.300 --> 01:01:21.540
Please. try to understand..
- Please! Go away!

711
01:01:21.620 --> 01:01:22.340
Big brother..?

712
01:01:25.660 --> 01:01:26.820
What's the matter. big brother?

713
01:01:27.700 --> 01:01:29.140
Big brother? Stop that farce!

714
01:01:29.860 --> 01:01:33.220
Sapna belongs to a respectable family.
And she is my guest.

715
01:01:33.700 --> 01:01:36.540
If you even set your
sights on her again..

716
01:01:40.540 --> 01:01:41.620
I'll kill you!

717
01:01:43.220 --> 01:01:46.580
I'm sorry big brother.
I can't promise.

718
01:01:52.580 --> 01:01:54.380
You will flirt with her. will you?

719
01:01:55.220 --> 01:01:57.900
Big brother. I respect you a lot.

720
01:01:58.580 --> 01:02:01.780
But I love Sapna lot
more than I respect you.

721
01:02:08.740 --> 01:02:10.180
You want to seduce her!
And you say you love her?

722
01:02:16.020 --> 01:02:19.180
Who do you think you are?
I'm no cheapskate.

723
01:02:20.140 --> 01:02:21.140
I'm Raghuveer Singh Chauhan's son.

724
01:02:21.220 --> 01:02:22.660
The only heir to Raghuveer Industries.

725
01:02:22.740 --> 01:02:23.700
Liar!

726
01:02:25.340 --> 01:02:26.820
I'm not lying. big brother.

727
01:02:27.420 --> 01:02:30.980
The Rajput mansion
in this city belongs to me.

728
01:02:31.180 --> 01:02:34.380
Lying again?
It belongs to Savitri Devi

729
01:02:41.260 --> 01:02:44.620
Savitri Devi is my mother.

730
01:02:47.220 --> 01:02:51.220
Now you'll say that I'm lying.
Let me ask you something

731
01:02:51.900 --> 01:02:54.740
Can you prove that your
mother is really your mother?

732
01:02:55.580 --> 01:02:56.300
Answer me.

733
01:02:58.420 --> 01:02:59.540
Tell me.

734
01:03:39.620 --> 01:03:41.380
I'm leaving your hotel.

735
01:03:43.460 --> 01:03:45.100
Not this city.

736
01:03:45.940 --> 01:03:51.460
Do what you want.
But I'm not going away from Sapna.

737
01:03:55.140 --> 01:03:57.420
Just what I wanted to hear from you.

738
01:03:58.060 --> 01:04:00.620
I wanted to know
how much you love her.

739
01:04:01.420 --> 01:04:05.460
I now believe. you love her dearly.

740
01:04:07.380 --> 01:04:12.460
By the way. I trusted you.
but deep inside. I suspected.

741
01:04:13.220 --> 01:04:19.140
That's why I had to put you to test.
Forgive me. Raja.

742
01:04:20.620 --> 01:04:21.380
Raja.

743
01:04:22.500 --> 01:04:23.420
I'm sorry.

744
01:04:30.180 --> 01:04:30.900
Sure.

745
01:04:44.860 --> 01:04:48.300
Frankly speaking big brother.
you are an enigma.

746
01:04:49.260 --> 01:04:51.260
I don't understand you either.

747
01:04:51.660 --> 01:04:52.900
You left mother behind..

748
01:04:52.980 --> 01:04:55.940
I mean how could you
leave your mother and come here?

749
01:04:56.700 --> 01:04:58.060
Who will take care of her?

750
01:05:01.620 --> 01:05:06.740
Point. Everything was
fine while Daddy was alive.

751
01:05:08.060 --> 01:05:10.020
He passed away four years ago.

752
01:05:14.860 --> 01:05:19.900
Ever since. I never left mother alone.

753
01:05:20.940 --> 01:05:25.540
But I couldn't help it.
She was after me to get married.

754
01:05:25.620 --> 01:05:28.580
Had I not run away.
I'd have been married by now.

755
01:05:29.660 --> 01:05:32.500
Think big brother.
What would've happened to Sapna?

756
01:05:33.260 --> 01:05:34.980
Who would've married her?

757
01:05:36.700 --> 01:05:38.460
Just okay.

758
01:05:39.300 --> 01:05:43.380
Thousands might be
dreaming about marrying her.

759
01:05:46.380 --> 01:05:49.380
But I dream of her everyday.

760
01:05:50.380 --> 01:05:55.140
I fear. should my dream shatter.
how will I survive?

761
01:05:56.540 --> 01:05:57.860
If I could get one picture of her..

762
01:05:57.940 --> 01:06:02.500
Why don't you introduce her to mother?

763
01:06:02.740 --> 01:06:04.100
You're strange. big brother.

764
01:06:04.340 --> 01:06:06.100
I haven't yet been
introduced to her properly.

765
01:06:06.180 --> 01:06:07.500
And you ask me to
introduce her to mother?

766
01:06:08.300 --> 01:06:11.140
I don't even know if she likes me.

767
01:06:11.500 --> 01:06:14.460
What if she refuses to meet mother?
- She won't.

768
01:06:15.260 --> 01:06:20.220
Not consolation. I need your help.
Just help me once. please.

769
01:06:20.420 --> 01:06:23.940
She lives in your house.
she heeds you too.

770
01:06:24.020 --> 01:06:26.300
Tell her that I'm a gentleman.

771
01:06:27.060 --> 01:06:30.700
That might just hit home.
Please. - I'll talk to her.

772
01:06:31.060 --> 01:06:34.260
Thank you. Thank you big brother.
thank you very much.

773
01:06:34.340 --> 01:06:38.340
Listen.. call mother over. quickly.
- Right away.

774
01:06:50.940 --> 01:06:54.540
Hello. - Hello mother? Raja here.

775
01:06:54.940 --> 01:06:59.260
Raja! Hopeless idiot!

776
01:06:59.340 --> 01:07:01.660
Ass! Fraud! Where have you been?

777
01:07:02.980 --> 01:07:05.780
For all these days of not
keeping in touch. she's blessing me.

778
01:07:05.900 --> 01:07:08.580
How long will you pursue that girl?
- Mother.

779
01:07:09.500 --> 01:07:11.500
I'm here only to meet her. Mother

780
01:07:11.580 --> 01:07:15.420
Yes. I've met her.
Come over at once. mother.

781
01:07:15.500 --> 01:07:16.780
I want to introduce her to you.

782
01:07:16.860 --> 01:07:19.060
Ass! Where are you? - What?

783
01:07:19.140 --> 01:07:23.460
Where are you?
- In Dharampur. I'm staying in a hotel

784
01:07:23.540 --> 01:07:25.180
We got such a huge
ancestral mansion there.

785
01:07:25.260 --> 01:07:26.340
And you're staying in a hotel?

786
01:07:26.580 --> 01:07:30.020
Ma. how can I stay
alone in that huge mansion?

787
01:07:30.100 --> 01:07:31.460
You haven't a cent on you.

788
01:07:31.540 --> 01:07:33.700
How could you stay
in a hotel all these days?

789
01:07:33.980 --> 01:07:38.420
Ma. I've found a brother..
a brother. in fact.

790
01:07:38.660 --> 01:07:41.860
I lovingly call him big brother.

791
01:07:42.740 --> 01:07:47.740
He's been so kind. One minute.
talk to him.. please talk to him.

792
01:07:51.060 --> 01:07:51.820
Hello.

793
01:07:52.220 --> 01:07:55.300
Hello son. - Mother..

794
01:07:56.380 --> 01:07:59.860
..you're coming. aren't you?
- I'll be coming come over. soon.

795
01:07:59.940 --> 01:08:04.100
Son. do you know the
girl Raja is talking about?

796
01:08:04.980 --> 01:08:06.020
Hello.

797
01:08:07.820 --> 01:08:09.020
Hello.

798
01:08:09.380 --> 01:08:16.380
Son. are you listening?
I said.. - Yes mother. I know her.

799
01:08:16.460 --> 01:08:18.780
She's very nice.

800
01:08:21.500 --> 01:08:23.660
Mother. come over quickly.

801
01:08:23.859 --> 01:08:25.619
Okay darling.

802
01:08:25.700 --> 01:08:27.300
Bye. - Okay bye.

803
01:08:28.500 --> 01:08:31.620
What's the matter. big brother?
You're in tears?

804
01:08:32.580 --> 01:08:35.540
What happened. brother?
- I talked to mother..

805
01:08:36.540 --> 01:08:38.020
Just couldn't help the tears.

806
01:08:46.260 --> 01:08:49.300
Why are you boozing so much?
You had quit drinking. hadn't you?

807
01:08:50.660 --> 01:08:55.020
If not tonight. when will I drink?
I've talked to my mother today!

808
01:08:55.180 --> 01:09:00.580
I have found my brother! Know how
he spoke to mother about Sapna?

809
01:09:01.020 --> 01:09:04.220
He loves her dearly.
- And the love that you have for her?

810
01:09:04.420 --> 01:09:07.980
My love for her..?
Sealed inside my heart.

811
01:09:08.660 --> 01:09:10.740
Good that Sapna doesn't know.

812
01:09:13.380 --> 01:09:15.780
Now I'm going to
talk to her about Raja.

813
01:09:15.979 --> 01:09:17.219
For all you've been doing for him..

814
01:09:17.620 --> 01:09:19.820
..why don't you tell
him you're his brother?

815
01:09:21.460 --> 01:09:24.580
When mother hasn't told
him about me. how..

816
01:09:27.979 --> 01:09:30.059
Why hasn't mother told him about me?

817
01:09:32.700 --> 01:09:34.100
When she comes over I'll ask her..

818
01:09:34.180 --> 01:09:35.620
