always happen with you?

823
01:09:57.940 --> 01:10:02.220
Now don't cry. okay?
Tonight I'm overjoyed.

824
01:10:02.500 --> 01:10:06.260
Get up. let's go elsewhere
and booze. Come on.

825
01:10:06.340 --> 01:10:08.300
