Jogi. he seems to be an astrologer.

832
01:10:35.420 --> 01:10:37.460
Greetings. - Goodbye.

833
01:10:38.460 --> 01:10:42.740
He's a coward.
- Fight if you're born of your mother!

834
01:10:47.140 --> 01:10:50.220
Amazing. You know my history.

835
01:10:52.140 --> 01:10:56.420
I know I am born of her.
but my mother thinks otherwise.

836
01:10:56.500 --> 01:10:57.300
