838
01:11:44.020 --> 01:11:46.540
My mother is a Goddess!

839
01:12:11.420 --> 01:12:15.540
Forgive me.
- A mother is a mother. no matter what.

840
01:12:18.220 --> 01:12:20.620
Don't.. - A mother is a mother!

841
