867
01:15:00.180 --> 01:15:04.060
Raja is a nice boy.

868
01:15:04.980 --> 01:15:08.620
And he's madly in love with you.

869
01:15:09.860 --> 01:15:11.100
He loves you dearly.

870
01:15:23.500 --> 01:15:26.540
Winning a girl's
heart is as much a..

871
01:15:26.620 --> 01:15:28.380
..difficult task as it is easy. Raja.

872
01:15:28.900 --> 01:15:33.620
She could flip in a moment.
She could even take months to decide.

873
