Brilliant idea mother!

985
01:28:05.660 --> 01:28:11.060
Are you mad? Sapna isn't
a doll that I'll inspect and try out.

986
01:28:12.020 --> 01:28:15.620
Since you and Suraj like her.
I too must like her.

987
01:28:15.940 --> 01:28:18.780
Yes son. I'd like to see her once.

988
01:28:19.300 --> 01:28:20.660
Why not organize a party?

989
01:28:20.900 --> 01:28:22.500
That'd give me an
opportunity to meet her.

990
01:28:22.580 --> 01:28:24.460
Brilliant idea mother!

991
01:28:25.980 --> 01:28:27.380
Holy offerings. madam. - Thanks.

992
01:28:28.380 --> 01:28:29.700
Here Eat.

993
01:28:31.620 --> 01:28:33.740
Here.. no. let me feed you. son.

994
01:28:46.900 --> 01:28:48.420
So long time.

995
01:28:49.020 --> 01:28:52.580
Suraj. she is Sapna. isn't she?
- Yes mother.

996
01:28:53.220 --> 01:28:54.900
Sapna.. - Mother.

997
01:28:55.700 --> 01:28:56.660
Greetings.

998
01:29:02.420 --> 01:29:05.820
Go on. dear. Raja is over there.

999
01:29:06.460 --> 01:29:07.380
Yes.

1000
01:29:07.460 --> 01:29:10.340
Suppose a fairy comes down to..

1001
01:29:10.420 --> 01:29:12.940
..earth in the form of a girl.
what would you do?

1002
01:29:13.860 --> 01:29:14.660
There she is.

1003
01:29:14.740 --> 01:29:17.460
See.. ladies and ladies.

1004
01:29:17.660 --> 01:29:20.420
My love my life.. My fairy.

1005
01:29:21.260 --> 01:29:25.540
What'd you have done
had Sapna not fallen for you?

1006
01:29:25.620 --> 01:29:27.500
I'd have married you.

1007
01:29:30.420 --> 01:29:33.180
You left the city as
if you vanished into thin air.

1008
01:29:34.020 --> 01:29:36.740
I had to leave for business' sake.

1009
01:29:37.020 --> 01:29:38.860
And had to return for Raja's sake.

1010
01:29:38.940 --> 01:29:42.060
Had to. for the sake
of my only son's happiness.

1011
01:29:42.820 --> 01:29:45.340
Yes you are right.

1012
01:30:58.900 --> 01:31:01.420
Raja. why did Suraj..?

1013
01:31:03.540 --> 01:31:09.020
Happiness eludes him. mother.
Some old wound must've resurfaced.

1014
01:31:11.140 --> 01:31:12.620
He gives his love to the world.

1015
01:31:13.660 --> 01:31:18.540
But he has gained nothing but anguish.

1016
01:31:26.620 --> 01:31:30.460
"My tears. I have suppressed"

1017
01:31:30.620 --> 01:31:34.500
"My life has been miserable.."

1018
01:31:34.580 --> 01:31:42.420
"Oh. how do I say how
helpless how I've been.."

1019
01:31:42.660 --> 01:31:50.260
"You are so near. yet so far.."

1020
01:31:50.340 --> 01:31:54.540
"I want to you call you mother.."

1021
01:31:54.620 --> 01:31:58.580
"I wish to embrace you.."

1022
01:31:58.660 --> 01:32:02.020
"Oh. how do I tell you.."

1023
01:32:02.100 --> 01:32:08.380
"My constraints.."

1024
01:32:08.580 --> 01:32:12.580
"My constraints.."

1025
01:32:12.660 --> 01:32:16.420
"My constraints.."

1026
01:32:44.820 --> 01:32:50.740
You are my son. Sonu.

1027
01:32:57.660 --> 01:32:58.300
Mother.

1028
01:33:02.020 --> 01:33:07.900
Which means your father
lied to me that you were..

1029
01:33:12.660 --> 01:33:13.580
My son.

1030
01:33:21.180 --> 01:33:22.340
My darling.

1031
01:33:27.780 --> 01:33:32.020
My boy.. my son.

1032
01:33:53.140 --> 01:33:53.780
Mother..

1033
01:33:53.980 --> 01:33:57.940
Go away.. get out of my sight!

1034
01:33:59.380 --> 01:34:03.300
When will you stop chasing me?
Get out of here. I say!

1035
01:34:05.140 --> 01:34:09.100
Do you know how much
I hate your very sight?

1036
01:34:09.180 --> 01:34:13.740
Why do you hate me. mother?
Since childhood I've been pining..

1037
01:34:13.820 --> 01:34:20.460
..and searching for an answer.
What makes you detest me?

1038
01:34:21.860 --> 01:34:25.660
Why do you hate me? Tell me. why?

1039
01:34:25.740 --> 01:34:31.540
Because you're not human.
You are a monster!

1040
01:34:33.980 --> 01:34:37.580
Yograj! - Yograj..?

1041
01:34:37.780 --> 01:34:43.220
You're a beast! You have
no right to live among humans!

1042
01:34:43.500 --> 01:34:48.340
You ought to be behind bars!
And I shall get you behind bars.

1043
01:34:48.900 --> 01:34:50.820
Your Honour..

1044
01:34:50.900 --> 01:34:53.860
I have witnessed this devil's crime.

1045
01:34:55.900 --> 01:34:59.780
I saw it! He raped that poor girl..

1046
01:35:00.060 --> 01:35:04.140
..and then mercilessly
slit the innocent's throat.

1047
01:35:04.860 --> 01:35:10.380
Look at him. Your Honour.
Look at that vicious grin.

1048
01:35:11.620 --> 01:35:15.620
But I'm not afraid of him.
Despite his threats..

1049
01:35:15.700 --> 01:35:19.540
..I have come to the court
so that justice may be done.

1050
01:35:28.460 --> 01:35:30.860
You are so lonely. Savitri.

1051
01:35:31.740 --> 01:35:34.260
It's such a big world.
but you have no one to call your own.

1052
01:35:35.540 --> 01:35:37.500
But you have a very big house.

1053
01:35:41.940 --> 01:35:46.540
Should any window or door squeak..

1054
01:35:47.980 --> 01:35:50.340
..do not dismiss it as mere breeze.

1055
01:35:52.020 --> 01:35:55.620
The tempest could
strike your door anytime.

1056
01:35:57.860 --> 01:36:01.180
I think the death sentence
has driven you insane.

1057
01:36:01.500 --> 01:36:03.420
You're daydreaming.

1058
01:36:04.900 --> 01:36:07.060
Revenge is a far cry. Yograj.

1059
01:36:07.420 --> 01:36:10.780
After this day you will yearn
to breathe the air of freedom.

1060
01:36:13.740 --> 01:36:16.100
When were you released. Yograj?

1061
01:36:17.460 --> 01:36:18.740
Don't step forward. Yograj.

1062
01:36:21.340 --> 01:36:22.060
Don't.

1063
01:36:44.060 --> 01:36:44.780
Ma..

1064
01:36:47.220 --> 01:36:50.060
Mr. Chauhan.
after your fiancée slipped into coma..

1065
01:36:50.140 --> 01:36:51.460
..we found out that she is pregnant

1066
01:36:51.540 --> 01:36:56.860
I don't want a demon's baby!
I don't want the devil!

1067
01:36:57.900 --> 01:37:00.900
Calm down. - Leave me.

1068
01:37:01.420 --> 01:37:03.420
Injection please. Savitri relax.

1069
01:37:03.660 --> 01:37:06.780
Relax. Nothing will
happen to you. Please.

1070
01:37:07.420 --> 01:37:09.420
No doctor. Please!

1071
01:37:10.100 --> 01:37:12.620
Savitri relax.

1072
01:37:13.380 --> 01:37:14.140
Savitri..

1073
01:37:15.940 --> 01:37:17.060
Savitri..

1074
01:37:24.060 --> 01:37:25.300
Mr. Chauhan. - Doctor. that..

1075
01:37:25.860 --> 01:37:26.940
No Mr. Chauhan.
abortion is impossible..

1076
01:37:27.820 --> 01:37:31.460
..It's more than seven months.

1077
01:37:32.780 --> 01:37:34.300
Must do a Caesarean. prematurely.

1078
01:37:35.380 --> 01:37:37.860
Safest option for mother and baby.

1079
01:37:38.540 --> 01:37:42.140
My son.. my darling.

1080
01:37:47.660 --> 01:37:48.860
My son.

1081
01:37:52.180 --> 01:37:52.860
My darling.

1082
01:37:56.900 --> 01:38:00.020
Son. you are my son.

1083
01:38:01.620 --> 01:38:03.180
My son!

1084
01:38:08.380 --> 01:38:09.540
No..

1085
01:38:12.300 --> 01:38:13.900
No. this is not my baby!

1086
01:38:15.140 --> 01:38:18.620
No. you are not my son!

1087
01:38:19.700 --> 01:38:21.740
You are the scoundrel's bad blood.

1088
01:38:22.940 --> 01:38:24.900
You are born of me. no doubt but..

1089
01:38:25.820 --> 01:38:29.100
..the lecher's blood
runs in your veins.

1090
01:38:31.180 --> 01:38:31.860
And now..

1091
01:38:34.020 --> 01:38:39.860
I can see his face clearly.

1092
01:38:42.700 --> 01:38:43.660
You are him!

1093
01:38:45.540 --> 01:38:46.700
Yograj.

1094
01:38:49.020 --> 01:38:51.820
Which is why you are
laughing at me aren't you?

1095
01:38:53.260 --> 01:38:55.140
You are laughing at me.

1096
01:38:56.860 --> 01:39:03.460
I won't spare you.
I won't spare the mark of sin!

1097
01:39:03.540 --> 01:39:07.340
Take him away!
Get him out of my sight.

1098
01:39:07.420 --> 01:39:12.460
I don't want to see his face!
I don't want this baby.

1099
01:39:12.620 --> 01:39:16.420
I don't want this baby.

1100
01:39:26.220 --> 01:39:29.500
Mr Raja.
if she doesn't come around soon..

1101
01:39:29.580 --> 01:39:31.140
..her life could be in danger.

1102
01:39:31.660 --> 01:39:33.660
I think she has received
a terrible shock.

1103
01:39:33.740 --> 01:39:38.380
What shock. doctor? Impossible.
She was fine and happy yesterday.

1104
01:39:38.740 --> 01:39:41.780
How come all of a sudden..?
- No. this is not a sudden shock.

1105
01:39:42.300 --> 01:39:44.860
I think she has had these
kind of bouts before too.

1106
01:39:48.700 --> 01:39:51.740
Have you contacted your
family doctor? - Not yet.

1107
01:39:52.340 --> 01:39:56.700
He's attending a conference
in America. But we're trying.

1108
01:39:56.780 --> 01:40:00.020
Please contact him
as soon as possible. Ok.

1109
01:40:04.380 --> 01:40:08.780
What the doctor says just beats me.

1110
01:40:15.860 --> 01:40:20.300
Let it be dark. Father.
I can't stand the light.

1111
01:40:24.420 --> 01:40:28.340
I know you are extremely hurt. son.

1112
01:40:30.940 --> 01:40:37.820
But to stand the pain God
has give you a strong heart. too.

1113
01:40:39.700 --> 01:40:41.940
You must step out
of the darkness. son.

1114
01:40:43.700 --> 01:40:45.700
You got to search the
path of happiness on your own.

1115
01:40:46.540 --> 01:40:49.580
How is my mother? - Same as before.

1116
01:40:50.700 --> 01:40:55.140
The doctor it is imperative
that she comes around. else..

1117
01:40:55.220 --> 01:40:59.780
Nothing is happening to my mother.
Nothing! She'll be fine

1118
01:41:01.140 --> 01:41:04.700
Goddess Mother.
I never understood you.

1119
01:41:06.020 --> 01:41:09.460
But you know me.

1120
01:41:10.500 --> 01:41:13.500
Please help my mother recover.

1121
01:41:30.940 --> 01:41:34.540
Big brother.
you never fail to surprise me.

1122
01:41:36.020 --> 01:41:39.740
Every time you come up with
something that has no real reasons.

1123
01:41:41.500 --> 01:41:46.100
I could never imagine
you wouldn't come to see mother.

1124
01:41:47.780 --> 01:41:51.260
Though I felt like coming.
I couldn't gather enough courage.

1125
01:41:52.180 --> 01:41:54.100
I can't see her in this state.

1126
01:41:55.060 --> 01:41:56.700
Why did she go to your house?

1127
01:41:57.620 --> 01:42:00.620
I walked out of the party.
and she felt bad.

1128
01:42:01.020 --> 01:42:02.580
So she came to call me back.

1129
01:42:03.460 --> 01:42:07.340
But what happened there that
gave her such a terrible shock?

1130
01:42:08.460 --> 01:42:10.340
That's the question worrying me.

1131
01:42:10.740 --> 01:42:13.460
I don't know why she started yelling.

1132
01:42:14.340 --> 01:42:17.700
But Suraj.. - Forget it.

1133
01:42:18.580 --> 01:42:20.860
Tell me. how is mother?

1134
01:42:22.980 --> 01:42:24.980
She is very serious. big brother.

1135
01:42:26.020 --> 01:42:29.420
She hasn't closed
her eyes once in two days.

1136
01:42:30.100 --> 01:42:34.020
She is as inert as a rock.

1137
01:42:35.300 --> 01:42:38.700
Doctors say she's
in a very critical state.

1138
01:42:39.820 --> 01:42:41.900
If she doesn't come around..

1139
01:42:51.860 --> 01:42:52.460
Go son.

1140
01:42:53.900 --> 01:42:54.860
Go on

1141
01:43:32.820 --> 01:43:36.420
"The earth has gone to sleep"

1142
01:43:36.740 --> 01:43:40.420
"The skies have gone to sleep"

1143
01:43:40.740 --> 01:43:48.500
"Deep in the slumber
is the whole world"

1144
01:43:48.820 --> 01:43:52.660
"With dreams in her eyes.."

1145
01:43:52.820 --> 01:43:56.700
"Rocking you in her arms.."

1146
01:43:56.780 --> 01:44:02.420
"Your mother sings
a lullaby for you.."

1147
01:44:02.700 --> 01:44:10.700
"So come. sleep.."

1148
01:44:10.860 --> 01:44:14.780
"Come. slumber"

1149
01:44:30.940 --> 01:44:34.580
"I have no one but you"

1150
01:44:34.900 --> 01:44:38.860
"You are my only support"

1151
01:44:38.940 --> 01:44:46.740
"Without you. I might do the worst"

1152
01:44:46.940 --> 01:44:54.700
"I can't live all by myself. I'll die"

1153
01:44:54.780 --> 01:45:02.740
"Take me in your arms. embrace me"

1154
01:45:02.980 --> 01:45:12.740
"For God's sake.
Ma. don't make me cry"

1155
01:45:12.940 --> 01:45:16.980
"Don't bring me to tears"

1156
01:45:17.060 --> 01:45:21.100
"Come to me"

1157
01:45:31.740 --> 01:45:33.220
I told you. didn't I?

1158
01:45:34.860 --> 01:45:40.660
I hate the sight of you!
Get out! Get out of here!

1159
01:45:40.860 --> 01:45:44.220
Get out!

1160
01:45:46.060 --> 01:45:48.820
Nonsense!
It's a lie. Yograj cannot die!

1161
01:45:48.900 --> 01:45:50.340
Suraj. please.

1162
01:45:50.780 --> 01:45:52.420
You cannot bring alive a dead man.

1163
01:45:52.500 --> 01:45:54.100
Police records clearly state that..

1164
01:45:54.180 --> 01:45:55.780
..that man died. - In an accident?

1165
01:45:55.860 --> 01:45:57.820
Right. - His corpse was not found.

1166
01:45:57.980 --> 01:46:00.420
It happens. Suraj.
- It is also possible that..

1167
01:46:00.580 --> 01:46:05.260
..this is Yograj's ploy to
evade the police. Look at this.

1168
01:46:06.020 --> 01:46:08.540
Not a single picture of his..

1169
01:46:08.860 --> 01:46:10.340
..in the entire file.
No proofs. no leads.

1170
01:46:10.420 --> 01:46:14.620
Some pages are torn out.
If he is dead. then who did all this?

1171
01:46:15.100 --> 01:46:16.860
No matter what the police say..

1172
01:46:16.940 --> 01:46:20.180
Yograj cannot die before
my mother's humiliation is avenged.

1173
01:46:20.780 --> 01:46:21.820
Relax. Suraj.

1174
01:46:22.140 --> 01:46:23.740
I'll request the commissioner for..

1175
01:46:24.260 --> 01:46:27.900
..his consent to reopen Yograj's case.

1176
01:46:31.100 --> 01:46:35.580
Any more questions?
- No sir. Thank you.

1177
01:46:35.820 --> 01:46:37.420
Excuse me sir..

1178
01:46:37.940 --> 01:46:40.900
May I ask you few questions.
sir? - Go on

1179
01:46:41.420 --> 01:46:44.100
It is said the elections
for ministers..

1180
01:46:44.180 --> 01:46:45.700
..and the legislators are rigged.

1181
01:46:46.460 --> 01:46:50.020
Wrong. They can't be sold or bought.

1182
01:46:51.580 --> 01:46:53.180
It is those whom the public elect..

1183
01:46:53.260 --> 01:46:54.340
..who form the government.

1184
01:46:55.260 --> 01:46:57.820
Yes to set up majority
when there is none..

1185
01:46:57.900 --> 01:47:02.260
..we summon up like-thinking
people together. That's it.

1186
01:47:02.460 --> 01:47:03.860
One more request. sir.

1187
01:47:06.060 --> 01:47:06.900
Tell me.

1188
01:47:07.300 --> 01:47:10.340
I want to take some pictures
of you for our magazine.

1189
01:47:11.620 --> 01:47:16.420
I wish to take some pictures
of you for our magazine.

1190
01:47:19.140 --> 01:47:20.140
Come in the evening.

1191
01:47:20.220 --> 01:47:21.580
Ok sir. thank you.

1192
01:47:23.220 --> 01:47:25.100
Himmat is on the line. Thakur sir.

1193
01:47:27.380 --> 01:47:30.060
Go on. Himmat.
- You have risen from the dead.

1194
01:47:30.140 --> 01:47:33.060
What nonsense!
- Your case that had atrophied..

1195
01:47:33.740 --> 01:47:37.700
has been reopened. - What..?

1196
01:47:41.540 --> 01:47:43.900
Who did that? - Inspector Khan did.

1197
01:47:44.660 --> 01:47:48.900
On his friend. Suraj's say-so.
Suraj. that eccentric.

1198
01:47:49.460 --> 01:47:52.940
It is also because of them
that my son Gogi is locked up.

1199
01:47:54.140 --> 01:47:57.060
No idea who reopened the case. but..

1200
01:47:57.140 --> 01:48:00.660
Himmat you always give me bad news.

1201
01:48:01.140 --> 01:48:04.500
And incomplete. - Why worry. sir?

1202
01:48:04.860 --> 01:48:09.300
Not even their angels can reach you.
- That's fine.

1203
01:48:09.940 --> 01:48:12.260
But precaution is better than cure.

1204
01:48:13.940 --> 01:48:14.620
But precaution is better than cure.
Kill them.

1205
01:48:15.100 --> 01:48:15.700
What?

1206
01:48:16.820 --> 01:48:17.700
Yes sir.

1207
01:48:20.940 --> 01:48:23.860
What did the Thakur say?
- Kill them both.

1208
01:48:24.140 --> 01:48:27.700
As if they were mere pigeons. Damn.

1209
01:48:36.620 --> 01:48:38.820
Just one minute.

1210
01:49:09.220 --> 01:49:10.460
What..? What are you doing. sir?

1211
01:49:13.420 --> 01:49:17.500
I'm a bad boy for you now.

1212
01:49:19.860 --> 01:49:21.900
I must be like a beast
coming at you - Sir..

1213
01:49:22.980 --> 01:49:24.060
A devil.

1214
01:49:26.620 --> 01:49:29.140
But try to understand my helplessness.

1215
01:49:30.380 --> 01:49:36.140
Ever since I saw you
the man within me has risen.

1216
01:49:36.220 --> 01:49:37.140
What are you doing. sir?

1217
01:49:37.580 --> 01:49:41.580
Sir. - You tell me. can I help it?

1218
01:49:41.740 --> 01:49:42.620
Let go. sir.

1219
01:49:44.100 --> 01:49:51.660
No sir. don't. Please let me go.

1220
01:49:51.740 --> 01:49:58.180
For God's sake. let me go. - No..

1221
01:50:54.780 --> 01:50:58.300
Yograj and his accomplice
Himmat have been bailed out.

1222
01:51:00.500 --> 01:51:02.060
Himmat and Yograj are friends..?

1223
01:51:07.220 --> 01:51:07.980
Suraj.

1224
01:53:00.780 --> 01:53:03.900
Are you all right. Suraj?
- They were his men. He's alive.

1225
01:53:04.420 --> 01:53:06.420
Yograj is alive. Ahmed. - Yes Suraj.

1226
01:53:07.180 --> 01:53:09.260
Himmat will take us to him.

1227
01:53:09.340 --> 01:53:11.660
Welcome.

1228
01:53:14.820 --> 01:53:19.780
Greetings. Thakur sir.
What brings you to Dharampur?

1229
01:53:19.860 --> 01:53:23.300
I couldn't refuse minister
Deshmukh's request.

1230
01:53:23.380 --> 01:53:24.820
How are you? - I'm fine.

1231
01:53:25.260 --> 01:53:27.180
I hear that you are
planning something..

1232
01:53:27.260 --> 01:53:28.940
..unique for the welfare of women.

1233
01:53:29.020 --> 01:53:31.260
You have heard it right. - Yes.

1234
01:53:31.860 --> 01:53:36.740
When it comes to women's welfare.
I'm always a step ahead - Ok.

1235
