I have some program for
their upliftment. - Yes. yes.

1239
01:53:48.820 --> 01:53:52.140
Let's see how God helps me. - Sure.

1240
01:53:52.220 --> 01:53:54.460
Okay. Salutations. - Salutations.

1241
