Does he know that I
had him attacked? Scoot!

1250
01:55:15.220 --> 01:55:16.940
Where is Himmat? - I don't know.

1251
01:55:17.020 --> 01:55:19.740
Where is he? - I really don't know.

1252
01:55:24.580 --> 01:55:28.140
Save me! Save me. Thakur sir.

1253
01:55:28.220 --> 01:55:31.420
Let go of me.
Who are you? - Don't you recognise me?

1254
01:55:31.700 --> 01:55:34.380
Then Suraj too won't recognise me.
I'm Himmat.

1255
01:55:34.460 --> 01:55:36.940
What farce is this. Himmat?
What has gotten into you?

1256
01:55:37.020 --> 01:55:39.660
Save me from the wounded tiger.

1257
01:55:39.740 --> 01:55:42.820
Else that Suraj will
give me a funeral.

1258
01:55:44.020 --> 01:55:47.940
Suraj..? But you said.. - I lied.

1259
