Good morning.

1271
01:56:33.540 --> 01:56:34.740
Good morning. doctor.

1272
01:56:34.820 --> 01:56:36.220
How are you? - Fine.

1273
01:56:36.300 --> 01:56:37.220
Very good.

1274
