Mr. Raja. you can take
your mother home if you want.

1275
01:56:40.860 --> 01:56:45.020
But you need complete bed rest.
Okay. - Okay.

1276
01:56:45.100 --> 01:56:47.820
She is very weak. Take care. bye.
- Okay. thank you Doctor.

1277
01:56:48.340 --> 01:56:51.540
Shall we. mother?
Let me take you home. - Let's go. son.

1278
01:56:55.420 --> 01:56:56.260
You're back?

1279
01:56:57.420 --> 01:56:58.060
Sapna.

1280
01:56:58.900 --> 01:57:01.380
I was bent on seeing you tonight.

1281
01:57:01.580 --> 01:57:04.060
What for?
- What's come over you. Suraj?

1282
01:57:04.300 --> 01:57:09.060
Me..? Nothing. - Why aren't
you your old self anymore?

1283
01:57:09.820 --> 01:57:14.260
Why do I feel you're trying
to hide something very serious..

1284
01:57:14.860 --> 01:57:17.220
