1326
02:00:09.860 --> 02:00:15.580
"It's a lovely evening
and my beloved is with me"

1327
02:00:15.660 --> 02:00:19.500
"Such a lovely evening
and our feelings are young"

1328
02:00:21.220 --> 02:00:26.740
"It's such a lovely evening
and we're young at heart"

1329
02:00:26.820 --> 02:00:32.580
"What better things could
I want for a friendship?"

1330
02:00:32.660 --> 02:00:38.980
"It's a lovely evening
and my beloved is with me"

1331
02:00:44.020 --> 02:00:51.420
"You are like the moonlight.
you are like a fairy.."

1332
02:00:51.500 --> 02:00:55.620
"..for poets. you are so inspiring"

1333
02:01:01.140 --> 02:01:06.820
"The sight of you
drove my heart crazy.."

1334
02:01:06.900 --> 02:01:12.580
"..and thus started a love-story"

1335
02:01:12.660 --> 02:01:16.580
"Colour. beauty and lovely dreams.."

1336
02:01:18.300 --> 02:01:23.900
"I have it all"

1337
02:01:24.180 --> 02:01:29.900
"What more could
I ask for to be happy?"

1338
02:01:29.980 --> 02:01:36.300
"It's a lovely evening
and my beloved is with me"

1339
02:02:04.140 --> 02:02:08.140
"Here's love.
passion and the beloved.."

1340
02:02:09.900 --> 02:02:15.700
"Here's love.
passion and the beloved.."

1341
02:02:27.060 --> 02:02:32.740
"My eyes express what my lips don't.."

1342
02:02:32.820 --> 02:02:38.460
"..my story is different
from everybody else's"

1343
02:02:38.540 --> 02:02:44.260
"I have fallen in love with anyone.."

1344
02:02:44.340 --> 02:02:49.980
"I've never ever allowed
the sweet agony to grip my heart"

1345
02:02:50.060 --> 02:02:53.980
"There's music.
there's melody. there's a song.."

1346
02:02:55.740 --> 02:03:01.060
"There's music.
there's melody. there's a song.."

1347
02:03:01.140 --> 02:03:06.900
"..what more can we want
