1348
02:03:06.980 --> 02:03:12.500
"It's a lovely evening
and my beloved is with me"

1349
02:03:12.780 --> 02:03:18.220
"What more could I want in life?"

1350
02:03:18.300 --> 02:03:23.860
"It's a lovely evening
and your beloved is with you"

1351
02:03:24.260 --> 02:03:30.060
"What more could you want in love?"

1352
02:03:45.820 --> 02:03:49.420
Mr Rajpal Thakur.
who is today in our midst..

1353
02:03:49.500 --> 02:03:53.300
..who will tell us how rapists
should be punished. Thakur sir.

1354
02:03:53.780 --> 02:03:58.860
Why does man forget that it
was a woman who gave birth to him?

1355
02:03:59.540 --> 02:04:01.980
Why does he make her
a victim of his lust?

1356
02:04:02.060 --> 02:04:05.420
Why does he outrage her modesty?
Why does he rape her?

1357
02:04:05.820 --> 02:04:09.580
In my opinion. rape is a
more heinous crime than even murder.

1358
02:04:10.820 --> 02:04:13.220
Because in a murder.
a woman dies only once.

1359
02:04:14.900 --> 02:04:19.500
Whereas rape inflicts death
on a woman every day of her life.

1360
02:04:20.420 --> 02:04:25.660
And a woman rues something
for which she was not to blame.

1361
02:04:32.460 --> 02:04:37.100
Woman is the greatest
boon God has granted to man.

1362
02:04:41.820 --> 02:04:43.660
We ought to worship her.

1363
02:04:46.300 --> 02:04:48.300
Love her.

1364
02:04:51.860 --> 02:04:53.900
Respect her.

1365
02:04:57.020 --> 02:05:01.740
A woman deserves a status
that is equal to God's.

1366
02:05:04.300 --> 02:05:09.820
However. there are monsters who.
blinded by lust..

1367
02:05:10.660 --> 02:05:13.820
try to violate a
woman's sacred honour.

1368
02:05:14.820 --> 02:05:16.580
For men who commits
such heinous crimes..

1369
02:05:16.660 --> 02:05:18.420
..a 7-year prison term is not enough.

1370
02:05:19.260 --> 02:05:21.500
They ought to be paraded..

1371
02:05:21.580 --> 02:05:23.180
..in the streets and shot dead.

1372
02:05:25.380 --> 02:05:26.300
Thank you.

1373
02:05:38.580 --> 02:05:41.300
This chap is Suraj.
the owner of this hotel.

1374
02:05:41.900 --> 02:05:43.860
He's the one who had your file..

1375
02:05:48.020 --> 02:05:50.140
In the applause of the others..

1376
02:05:50.220 --> 02:05:51.740
..I found true
appreciation for myself.

1377
02:05:52.580 --> 02:05:54.780
Your applause.
however. pokes fun at me.

1378
02:05:55.140 --> 02:05:57.220
That's what I think. - And I thought..

1379
02:05:57.300 --> 02:06:00.820
..that your face wasn't in
sync with what you were saying.

1380
02:06:02.220 --> 02:06:06.020
Don't you think shooting such
men will make death easy for them?

1381
02:06:06.420 --> 02:06:08.300
So how should such men be punished?

1382
02:06:09.980 --> 02:06:12.340
A man like that ought
to be tortured to death.

1383
02:06:13.300 --> 02:06:17.580
He ought to be blinded for
casting a lustful look at a woman.

1384
02:06:18.140 --> 02:06:20.060
His hands ought to be severed..

1385
02:06:20.780 --> 02:06:24.300
..the hands that violated
a woman's honour.

1386
02:06:25.260 --> 02:06:29.820
He should be publicly whipped.
so much that..

1387
02:06:29.900 --> 02:06:33.140
..he begs for pardon.

1388
02:06:39.740 --> 02:06:43.980
You have indeed thought
of a great punishment.

1389
02:06:45.660 --> 02:06:46.660
So much of hatred?

1390
02:06:48.660 --> 02:06:51.820
Any special reason
for so much of contempt?

1391
02:06:54.220 --> 02:06:59.220
Do you need a reason to
hold something evil in contempt..

1392
02:06:59.580 --> 02:07:02.500
Thakur. - Thakur sir

1393
02:07:04.900 --> 02:07:06.820
You are indeed an interesting man.

1394
02:07:08.020 --> 02:07:10.660
Your face isn't again
saying what your mouth is.

1395
02:07:11.820 --> 02:07:15.420
A man who speaks the truth
isn't interesting.. he's bitter.

1396
02:07:18.740 --> 02:07:22.420
Perhaps my face won't
again express what my lips do.

1397
02:07:24.620 --> 02:07:31.060
But I do like people like you.
- But I do not like you at all.

1398
02:07:33.900 --> 02:07:38.580
Why do you think I'm so bad?
This is our very first meeting.

1399
02:07:39.100 --> 02:07:44.700
No. Thakur sir. We are no strangers.
We have already met.

1400
02:07:48.100 --> 02:07:51.420
Where? - I don't know.

1401
02:07:52.980 --> 02:07:54.420
But we have surely met.

1402
02:09:51.580 --> 02:09:55.380
Why've you been looking for me?
What do you want from me?

1403
02:09:55.820 --> 02:09:56.820
Yograj!

1404
02:10:00.220 --> 02:10:04.540
Who..? - Your old friend. Yograj.

1405
02:10:05.660 --> 02:10:10.220
Kid. dead-men don't come back to life.

1406
02:10:10.420 --> 02:10:13.900
They do.
Just tell me his whereabouts..

1407
02:10:14.540 --> 02:10:16.460
..or I'll turn you
into a dead-man too.

1408
02:10:18.620 --> 02:10:21.020
Such guts to confront Himmat?

1409
02:10:22.060 --> 02:10:24.380
He has the guts. all right.

1410
02:10:27.220 --> 02:10:30.420
I'll give you an answer
to all your courage today.

1411
02:10:50.860 --> 02:10:51.620
Faster!

1412
02:10:52.340 --> 02:10:54.500
Thakur sir.
Suraj has escaped from my clutches.

1413
02:10:54.580 --> 02:10:57.780
I mean. I've escaped his clutches!
- I get it. Himmat.

1414
02:10:59.140 --> 02:11:00.740
This is not your cup of tea.

1415
02:11:02.060 --> 02:11:07.340
You can just watch how I
tame this ferocious tiger of yours.

1416
02:11:09.020 --> 02:11:09.820
Let's go.

1417
02:11:11.500 --> 02:11:16.060
Why don't you tell me?
These fits that mother suffers from..

1418
02:11:16.500 --> 02:11:17.740
..what's the reason?

1419
02:11:18.100 --> 02:11:21.380
As difficult as it
is for me to say it..

1420
02:11:23.380 --> 02:11:27.300
..it'll be more difficult
for you to hear it.

1421
02:11:34.500 --> 02:11:39.060
Many years ago. your mother
went through a terrible incident..

1422
02:11:39.780 --> 02:11:41.420
..I was on duty at the hospital then.

1423
02:12:03.780 --> 02:12:06.340
There was an unfortunate boy who was..

1424
02:12:06.420 --> 02:12:08.500
..separated from
us and abandoned here.

1425
02:12:09.380 --> 02:12:13.660
It was Suraj. wasn't it?

1426
02:12:17.780 --> 02:12:21.140
Big brother! Here I am!

1427
02:12:21.780 --> 02:12:27.340
Raja. Why have you called me here?

1428
02:12:27.420 --> 02:12:29.740
What I want to talk to you..

1429
02:12:30.620 --> 02:12:35.180
..about cannot be discussed
at the mansion nor at your house.

1430
02:12:36.180 --> 02:12:39.460
And I had to drink..

1431
02:12:39.940 --> 02:12:44.860
..because I couldn't have talked
about it in a sober state of mind.

1432
02:12:45.340 --> 02:12:46.420
I'm sorry.

1433
02:12:46.780 --> 02:12:51.980
What's so serious. Raja?
- Raja..? Already?

1434
02:12:53.660 --> 02:12:55.620
Won't you call me little brother?

1435
02:12:58.660 --> 02:13:00.220
Won't you embrace me?

1436
02:13:01.900 --> 02:13:03.500
Won't you hug me?

1437
02:13:09.140 --> 02:13:13.900
Your favors.
your love and your sacrifice..

1438
02:13:13.980 --> 02:13:19.140
I could understand nothing you do.
And today I realize..

1439
02:13:19.460 --> 02:13:25.220
how big the elder brother really is.
What say. brother?

1440
02:13:35.380 --> 02:13:38.900
Despite being brothers.
we have different destinies.

1441
02:13:40.340 --> 02:13:43.780
I get all the happiness
and you get all the sorrows.

1442
02:13:45.380 --> 02:13:52.740
I get the share of the joys..
and you get to share the woes.

1443
02:13:54.140 --> 02:13:55.780
I was the one who got
all of our mother's love.

1444
02:13:57.220 --> 02:14:00.740
And you.. you got only hatred.

1445
02:14:03.060 --> 02:14:08.980
You even pined to
hear mother call you son.

1446
02:14:10.220 --> 02:14:16.460
Brother. when I think of
what you've been through. I..

1447
02:14:21.540 --> 02:14:26.220
There is no problem now. Raja.
I have my brother with me.

1448
02:14:37.820 --> 02:14:41.620
If that is true.
why did Suraj give his letters to you?

1449
02:14:44.540 --> 02:14:48.660
Because he's my brother. Sapna.

1450
02:14:50.300 --> 02:14:51.860
For the sake of their
younger brothers..

1451
02:14:52.540 --> 02:14:55.500
..elder brothers often
sacrifice their joys.

1452
02:14:57.980 --> 02:15:02.060
Sapna. my brother has found
nothing but pain in his lifetime.

1453
02:15:05.980 --> 02:15:12.140
You know how ill-luck
has always followed him.

1454
02:15:13.780 --> 02:15:16.340
How can I pay back a brother
for the sacrifices he has made?

1455
02:15:20.940 --> 02:15:25.740
I want you to help me. Sapna.
Please help me.

1456
02:15:26.900 --> 02:15:30.340
Like I snatched his
mother from him as a child..

1457
02:15:32.140 --> 02:15:36.100
I don't want to snatch
his love from him today.

1458
02:15:36.300 --> 02:15:39.860
Sapna.. Sapna?

1459
02:16:31.140 --> 02:16:35.220
Suraj. will you tell
me the truth? - What?

1460
02:16:38.219 --> 02:16:39.859
Are you in love with me?

1461
02:16:44.340 --> 02:16:48.220
What sort of question is that?
- Straight and simple.

1462
02:16:49.459 --> 02:16:51.139
You were the one who said that..

1463
02:16:51.219 --> 02:16:53.219
..love makes for
a strange relationship.

1464
02:16:54.059 --> 02:16:55.299
That every relationship
in the world is..

1465
02:16:55.860 --> 02:16:57.660
..merged into this one relationship?

1466
02:16:59.379 --> 02:17:00.659
I want to know. Suraj.

1467
02:17:02.980 --> 02:17:06.300
All these letters..
did you write them for me?

1468
02:17:14.980 --> 02:17:16.820
Is love all that matters in life?

1469
02:17:17.580 --> 02:17:19.380
Does friendship amount to nothing?

1470
02:17:21.139 --> 02:17:22.739
How could you even
imagine such a thing?

1471
02:17:22.820 --> 02:17:24.580
What made you think like that?

1472
02:17:25.299 --> 02:17:26.659
Is it because of these letters..?

1473
02:17:26.740 --> 02:17:28.820
Because you see the name "Sapna" here?

1474
02:17:28.900 --> 02:17:31.060
Is there only one Sapna in this world?

1475
02:17:34.780 --> 02:17:37.140
It's a coincidence. The girl I was..

1476
02:17:37.580 --> 02:17:39.060
..in love with was also called Sapna.

1477
02:17:39.340 --> 02:17:42.980
What..? - She couldn't marry me.

1478
02:17:43.500 --> 02:17:44.580
She married someone else.

1479
02:17:46.340 --> 02:17:49.380
Anyway.. how was I
to know that my letters..

1480
02:17:49.459 --> 02:17:50.899
..would help my brother some day?

1481
02:17:55.980 --> 02:17:59.980
You are my best friend. And
you couldn't understand my feelings?

1482
02:18:03.379 --> 02:18:05.979
I'm sorry.

1483
02:18:09.219 --> 02:18:11.619
Gogi!

1484
02:18:11.980 --> 02:18:15.820
My son is here! The apple of my eye!

1485
02:18:16.100 --> 02:18:19.740
Himmat finds courage again!
- What Himmat?

1486
02:18:19.820 --> 02:18:21.580
What Himmat? What bloody Himmat!

1487
02:18:21.660 --> 02:18:23.820
Your courage went to sleep when..

1488
02:18:23.900 --> 02:18:25.460
..your son was doing
labour in prison?

1489
02:18:26.420 --> 02:18:30.460
When Inspector Khan and
Suraj were grinding my bones..

1490
02:18:30.540 --> 02:18:33.740
..to find out where my father was.
where was your courage?

1491
02:18:33.820 --> 02:18:39.140
It's me! Gogi!
I have endangered my life to get away.

1492
02:18:39.219 --> 02:18:40.739
Rascle. Himmat!

1493
02:18:43.139 --> 02:18:45.979
You are the one who escaped.
Gogi. - Yes.

1494
02:18:47.740 --> 02:18:48.900
What happened?

1495
02:18:52.139 --> 02:18:53.579
He's come to catch you!

1496
02:20:37.740 --> 02:20:39.700
He was our link to Yograj.

1497
02:21:06.660 --> 02:21:19.980
'Sanskrit chant'

1498
02:21:22.380 --> 02:21:26.580
'Sanskrit chant'

1499
02:21:34.140 --> 02:21:35.980
Yograj!

1500
02:21:40.500 --> 02:21:43.140
What are you doing..?
This is Thakur sir!

1501
02:21:43.220 --> 02:21:46.420
Leave him. Leave him! - Mother.

1502
02:21:47.140 --> 02:21:48.300
Nothing.

1503
02:21:48.380 --> 02:21:50.740
Yograj. - Mother!
It's okay.. I'm sorry sir.

1504
02:21:50.820 --> 02:21:52.980
This is Thakur-sir.
- I'm sorry. Thakur sir

1505
02:21:53.060 --> 02:21:57.740
Mother often has these fits.
She isn't well.

1506
02:21:57.940 --> 02:22:01.460
I am really sorry. Sorry.

1507
02:22:03.020 --> 02:22:07.740
Mother! He's not Yograj. mother.
It's Thakur.

1508
02:22:09.060 --> 02:22:11.460
It's Thakur.
Everything will be all right.

1509
02:22:11.540 --> 02:22:18.860
No. this is not a disguise!
I was burnt! By Suraj!

1510
02:22:18.940 --> 02:22:23.620
I'm glad I went a doctor on time.
As they truly say..

1511
02:22:23.700 --> 02:22:25.780
..doctors are like Gods.
One saved me..

1512
02:22:25.860 --> 02:22:28.980
..and even answered your question.

1513
02:22:29.060 --> 02:22:31.060
A question that always bothered you.

1514
02:22:31.140 --> 02:22:34.140
As to why Suraj is after your blood.

1515
02:22:35.740 --> 02:22:37.060
Gogi.

1516
02:22:38.300 --> 02:22:39.820
When I came to my senses.

1517
02:22:39.900 --> 02:22:43.580
I heard this doctor
saying something about Suraj.

1518
02:22:43.980 --> 02:22:48.620
I then put pressure
on him and got to know..

1519
02:22:49.940 --> 02:22:51.300
You tell him.

1520
02:23:00.380 --> 02:23:02.300
What do you know? Tell me.

1521
02:23:03.580 --> 02:23:10.500
He.. there was someone called
Yograj who had raped Savitri-devi.

1522
02:23:11.740 --> 02:23:14.540
Suraj is the offspring
of that outrage.

1523
02:23:46.020 --> 02:23:46.780
Doctor.

1524
02:23:50.580 --> 02:23:53.740
No one gives birth to
such illegitimate children.

1525
02:23:55.260 --> 02:24:02.500
They cause a lot of problems.
A lot of problems they cause!

1526
02:24:16.460 --> 02:24:18.540
I have a feeling that
this Thakur is Yograj.

1527
02:24:19.220 --> 02:24:21.420
Because whenever we
set out to find Yograj..

1528
02:24:21.500 --> 02:24:23.860
..we come across Thakur.

1529
02:24:24.500 --> 02:24:27.500
Okay. Suraj. On mere suspicion..
- We'll even find the evidence.

1530
02:24:27.900 --> 02:24:31.500
The guilt of a criminal
often implicates him.

1531
02:24:37.100 --> 02:24:38.500
Hello. - - Yograj.

1532
02:24:43.100 --> 02:24:45.100
Which Yograj? - The Yograj..

1533
02:24:46.060 --> 02:24:50.940
..who raped innumerable
girls in this very city..

1534
02:24:51.380 --> 02:24:52.740
..and then slit their throats.

1535
02:24:53.980 --> 02:24:56.420
You've got the wrong number.

1536
02:24:57.460 --> 02:24:59.140
There is no Yograj here.

1537
02:24:59.780 --> 02:25:01.180
This is Thakur Rajveer
Singh's residence.

1538
02:25:02.940 --> 02:25:07.660
Yograj. you can fool the
world as Thakur.. but not me

1539
02:25:08.420 --> 02:25:10.460
I've been looking
for you for many years.

1540
02:25:11.540 --> 02:25:14.060
And here you are.
- Haven't I told you?

1541
02:25:14.620 --> 02:25:17.180
I told you that you
are making a mistake.

1542
02:25:17.420 --> 02:25:19.740
I recognise your voice very well.

1543
02:25:19.940 --> 02:25:23.380
I have evidence of your dirty deeds.

1544
02:25:24.220 --> 02:25:29.380
I want a deal with you for your life.
For just 5 million rupees.

1545
02:25:30.580 --> 02:25:33.740
At 5 this evening.
come to table 10 at..

1546
02:25:34.140 --> 02:25:37.060
..the Royal Club. with the money.

1547
02:25:37.900 --> 02:25:40.940
Or else. I have other
buyers for those pictures.

1548
02:25:44.380 --> 02:25:49.060
Hello..

1549
02:26:03.660 --> 02:26:06.180
If he or any of his men gets there..

1550
02:26:06.940 --> 02:26:10.740
..it means Thakur is indeed Yograj.

1551
02:26:22.940 --> 02:26:25.620
Waiter. where is table number 10 ?
- It's right ahead. sir.

1552
02:27:07.020 --> 02:27:10.020
Where is Yograj? - Who's that?

1553
02:27:10.540 --> 02:27:11.660
Tell me.

1554
02:27:12.380 --> 02:27:13.620
Your Thakur..?

1555
02:27:14.580 --> 02:27:16.660
At the Home for Women.

1556
02:27:33.140 --> 02:27:33.900
Don't move.

1557
02:27:34.900 --> 02:27:38.100
Nobody moves from here.

1558
02:27:38.180 --> 02:27:39.500
You are all under arrest.

1559
02:27:39.580 --> 02:27:44.500
I have taken an oath that
this patriarchal society..

1560
02:27:44.580 --> 02:27:48.700
..which inflicts atrocities on women.
shall have..

1561
02:27:52.980 --> 02:27:54.180
shall..

1562
02:27:57.020 --> 02:27:58.020
shall..

1563
02:28:01.500 --> 02:28:02.580
shall..

1564
02:28:05.500 --> 02:28:06.620
Stop him!

1565
02:28:31.180 --> 02:28:32.780
Leave him! Leave him! I'll shoot you.

1566
02:29:17.180 --> 02:29:18.100
Stop!

1567
02:29:18.260 --> 02:29:19.420
Take him away!

1568
02:29:24.780 --> 02:29:26.220
It's okay. Are you alright sir?

1569
02:29:27.060 --> 02:29:30.420
Are you okay. Thakur sir..?
- He's crazy!

1570
02:29:41.940 --> 02:29:45.220
The first time I met you. I wondered..

1571
02:29:47.620 --> 02:29:53.940
..how a softie like Babu
could sire a fiery son like you.

1572
02:29:55.580 --> 02:30:00.300
And then I got to know..
that you're an illegitimate son.

1573
02:30:03.980 --> 02:30:08.620
What rage! Rage at the truth?

1574
02:30:10.220 --> 02:30:13.820
Suraj. your death
is a certainty today.

1575
02:30:15.940 --> 02:30:19.940
Why? Can't you see?

1576
02:30:21.660 --> 02:30:22.660
Take a good look.

1577
02:30:24.580 --> 02:30:27.940
Today. my face says
what my tongue says.

1578
02:30:28.940 --> 02:30:34.220
Hats off to you. You have
at last got to know that I'm Yograj.

1579
02:30:36.060 --> 02:30:38.740
People are scared of eye-balling.

1580
02:30:38.820 --> 02:30:40.700
Yograj and you had
the temerity to hit him.

1581
02:30:42.620 --> 02:30:45.220
That was a gross miscalculation
you made of my strength.

1582
02:30:45.460 --> 02:30:48.580
You are a coward and a spineless man.

1583
02:30:50.300 --> 02:30:52.940
You do know how to outrage
the modesty of a woman.

1584
02:30:54.020 --> 02:30:59.580
The acid that comes with
the offspring of your outrage..

1585
02:31:00.300 --> 02:31:04.500
..you do not have the courage to face.

1586
02:31:05.300 --> 02:31:07.140
No wonder you've had me tied up..

1587
02:31:07.220 --> 02:31:09.300
..to behave like an eunuch.

1588
02:31:10.460 --> 02:31:11.500
What did you say?

1589
02:31:15.420 --> 02:31:16.460
An eunuch?

1590
02:31:22.100 --> 02:31:26.220
Your very existence defies
what you just said. Suraj.

1591
02:31:28.420 --> 02:31:30.300
You are a spirited man. no doubt.

1592
02:31:32.660 --> 02:31:34.380
You have indeed taken
after your mother.

1593
02:31:36.420 --> 02:31:40.460
Know what?
She was a spirited lady too.

1594
02:31:42.980 --> 02:31:47.180
Like a glass of wine..
she was very intoxicating.

1595
02:31:49.380 --> 02:31:53.020
Like the Full Moon..
she was brimming with youth.

1596
02:31:55.540 --> 02:31:57.860
Like a dish that is boiling..

1597
02:31:59.340 --> 02:32:00.500
..she was hot.

1598
02:32:54.020 --> 02:32:55.820
Leave him.

1599
02:32:57.100 --> 02:32:57.860
Let go!

1600
02:32:58.900 --> 02:32:59.780
Leave.

1601
02:33:00.380 --> 02:33:01.340
Hit him.

1602
02:33:03.220 --> 02:33:04.500
Someone make him let go!

1603
02:33:15.700 --> 02:33:16.620
Get him!

1604
02:33:58.420 --> 02:34:00.620
Not your entire police force..

1605
02:34:00.700 --> 02:34:04.340
..could get your
hands on one unarmed man!

1606
02:34:04.700 --> 02:34:07.380
Shame on you!
0 We are doing our best. Thakur-sir

1607
02:34:07.460 --> 02:34:10.380
I don't want to listen
to anything! Shut up!

1608
02:34:11.900 --> 02:34:13.380
Find him. however you do it.

1609
02:34:14.100 --> 02:34:17.940
Before that dog can bite me.
hack him to pieces. Get that?

1610
02:34:18.260 --> 02:34:19.340
Very well. Thakur sir.

1611
02:34:20.340 --> 02:34:22.660
Get out of that place immediately.

1612
02:34:22.900 --> 02:34:24.180
S.P. Rana knows where you are..

1613
02:34:24.260 --> 02:34:26.180
..and he's out to kill you.
And listen. Suraj..

1614
02:34:26.340 --> 02:34:29.980
Thakur has been exposed
before the police.

1615
02:34:30.180 --> 02:34:32.620
His finger-prints have
proved that he's Yograj.

1616
02:34:32.700 --> 02:34:34.020
But he's absconding.

1617
02:34:57.820 --> 02:34:58.940
Recognise me..?

1618
02:35:00.620 --> 02:35:02.060
You don't even recognise
the father of..

1619
02:35:02.140 --> 02:35:04.340
..the illegitimate child you bore?

1620
02:35:05.460 --> 02:35:06.540
Yograj.

1621
02:35:31.500 --> 02:35:33.700
I'm going to kill you!

1622
02:35:35.940 --> 02:35:37.020
Yograj.

1623
02:35:38.220 --> 02:35:43.220
No one can kill me anymore. Savitri.
You are now in my custody.

1624
02:35:44.540 --> 02:35:46.780
I'm taking you to Delhi and no one..

1625
02:35:47.820 --> 02:35:50.500
..can do any harm to me out there.

1626
02:35:51.700 --> 02:35:55.060
Not even the one I fathered.

1627
02:35:56.620 --> 02:35:58.140
Drag her along!

1628
02:36:39.380 --> 02:36:39.860
Hello.

1629
02:36:40.020 --> 02:36:41.540
Raja? - Go on. Sapna.

1630
02:36:41.620 --> 02:36:44.660
Yograj has kidnapped mother.
- Yograj has kidnapped mother?

1631
02:36:44.900 --> 02:36:45.860
What..?

1632
02:36:46.980 --> 02:36:48.140
Hello. Suraj!

1633
02:36:48.580 --> 02:36:50.780
Mother has had a fit again. - What?

1634
02:36:50.860 --> 02:36:51.540
Yes.

1635
02:36:52.020 --> 02:36:55.380
Where are you right now?
- At Cart Road. following them.

1636
02:36:55.460 --> 02:36:57.140
At Cart Road..? - Yes.

1637
02:36:57.220 --> 02:36:58.380
All right.

1638
02:37:17.020 --> 02:37:18.420
Brother Carter Road.

1639
02:37:59.540 --> 02:38:01.500
Thakur sir! There's Suraj!

1640
02:38:02.700 --> 02:38:03.500
There they are. brother.

1641
02:38:05.100 --> 02:38:05.900
Blow them up!

1642
02:40:09.140 --> 02:40:11.220
What is this chaos? Move it!

1643
02:40:12.340 --> 02:40:15.620
What are you doing?
There is a traffic jam!

1644
02:40:17.340 --> 02:40:19.380
Move it! Move that truck!

1645
02:40:19.460 --> 02:40:21.060
Get out of the car!

1646
02:40:22.820 --> 02:40:26.060
Move!

1647
02:40:30.220 --> 02:40:31.220
Suraj!

1648
02:40:37.420 --> 02:40:39.340
Move out! Leave the car!

1649
02:40:39.660 --> 02:40:40.940
Hey come on!

1650
02:40:46.340 --> 02:40:48.100
Hey. move the car!

1651
02:41:45.340 --> 02:41:47.060
Attention. passengers.

1652
02:41:47.140 --> 02:41:49.980
Train on platform on number
one is headed for the yard.

1653
02:41:50.060 --> 02:41:52.900
Passengers are requested
not to board it.

1654
02:41:52.980 --> 02:41:55.340
Come on!
Else. I'll shoot both your sons.

1655
02:42:18.580 --> 02:42:21.820
Faster! The train
must stop only in Delhi!

1656
02:42:30.820 --> 02:42:32.140
Madhav.

1657
02:42:40.860 --> 02:42:42.260
Mother.

1658
02:42:48.540 --> 02:42:49.940
Mother.

1659
02:43:09.900 --> 02:43:11.100
Madhav Singh.

1660
02:47:09.700 --> 02:47:12.140
My son.. my son!

1661
02:47:12.500 --> 02:47:13.940
My darling son..

1662
02:47:14.340 --> 02:47:17.540
Come.. come to Papa

1663
02:47:20.460 --> 02:47:21.940
Come. my son.

1664
02:47:29.980 --> 02:47:31.220
You're hurt.

1665
02:47:32.780 --> 02:47:35.060
Come to Papa.. come. Here's another.

1666
02:47:44.460 --> 02:47:46.300
Come.

1667
02:47:48.900 --> 02:47:50.220
My son!

1668
02:47:52.180 --> 02:47:53.300
Suraj!

1669
02:47:55.060 --> 02:47:59.140
Kill this monster.. kill him!

1670
02:48:06.140 --> 02:48:09.140
Forgive me. my son! My son!

1671
02:48:09.500 --> 02:48:10.660
You are my son.

1672
02:48:11.620 --> 02:48:13.860
My blood flows in your veins.
- Shut up!

1673
02:48:16.060 --> 02:48:18.620
Only my mother's
blood flows in my veins.

1674
02:48:19.540 --> 02:48:22.620
And that blood seeks your blood.

1675
02:49:35.780 --> 02:49:36.740
Mother.

1676
02:49:37.780 --> 02:49:40.340
My son! Suraj.. - Mother!

1677
02:49:41.140 --> 02:49:43.620
No. - Mother.

1678
02:49:46.100 --> 02:49:47.900
Son Suraj.

1679
02:49:48.660 --> 02:49:53.460
My son. I owe you so much

1680
02:49:54.700 --> 02:49:59.460
I could never give you
the love you were entitled to

1681
02:50:01.660 --> 02:50:04.220
Forgive me. my son. - No. Mother

1682
02:50:05.540 --> 02:50:10.420
Don't say such things.
See? I'm happy today..

1683
02:50:11.260 --> 02:50:12.860
I lie in my mother's lap.

1684
02:50:13.305 --> 02:51:13.303
